                            h = f.group.length;
                        if (!(f.isDragging || f.isClosing || f.isAnimating && f.firstRun)) {

                    scaleToActual: function(t, e, o) {

                    },

                    },

                    },
                    update: function(t) {

                        n.each(e.slides, function(n, o) {
                            e.updateSlide(o, t)
                        })
                    },

                    },

                    },
                    isMoved: function(t) {

                    updateCursor: function(t, e) {

                    },
                    isZoomable: function() {
                        var t, e = this,
                            n = e.current;
                        if (n && !e.isClosing && "image" === n.type && !n.hasError) {
                            if (!n.isLoaded) return !0;
                            if ((t = e.getFitPos(n)) && (n.width > t.width || n.height > t.height)) return !0
                        }

                    },
                    isScaledDown: function(t, e) {
                        var i = !1,
                            a = this.current,
                            s = a.$content;
                        return void 0 !== t && void 0 !== e ? i = t < a.width && e < a.height : s && (i = (i = n.fancybox.getTranslate(s)).width < a.width && i.height < a.height), i
                    },
                    canPan: function(t, e) {

                            a = null,
                            s = !1;
                        return "image" === i.type && (i.isComplete || t && e) && !i.hasError && (s = this.getFitPos(i), void 0 !== t && void 0 !== e ? a = {
                            width: t,

                        } : i.isComplete && (a = n.fancybox.getTranslate(i.$content)), a && s && (s = 1.5 < Math.abs(a.width - s.width) || 1.5 < Math.abs(a.height - s.height))), s
                    },
                    loadSlide: function(t) {
                        var e, o, i, a = this;
                        if (!t.isLoading && !t.isLoaded) {
                            if (!(t.isLoading = !0) === a.trigger("beforeLoad", t)) return t.isLoading = !1;
                            switch (e = t.type, (o = t.$slide).off("refresh").trigger("onReset").addClass(t.opts.slideClass), e) {
                                case "image":
                                    a.setImage(t);
                                    break;
                                case "iframe":
                                    a.setIframe(t);
                                    break;
                                case "html":
                                    a.setContent(t, t.src || t.content);
                                    break;
                                case "video":
                                    a.setContent(t, t.opts.video.tpl.replace(/\{\{src\}\}/gi, t.src).replace("{{format}}", t.opts.videoFormat || t.opts.video.format || "").replace("{{poster}}", t.thumb || ""));
                                    break;
                                case "inline":
                                    n(t.src).length ? a.setContent(t, n(t.src)) : a.setError(t);
                                    break;
                                case "ajax":
                                    a.showLoading(t), i = n.ajax(n.extend({}, t.opts.ajax.settings, {
                                        url: t.src,
                                        success: function(e, n) {
                                            "success" === n && a.setContent(t, e)
                                        },
                                        error: function(e, n) {
                                            e && "abort" !== n && a.setError(t)
                                        }
                                    })), o.one("onReset", function() {
                                        i.abort()
                                    });
                                    break;
                                default:
                                    a.setError(t)
                            }
                            return !0
                        }
                    },
                    setImage: function(t) {
                        var o, i = this;
                        setTimeout(function() {
                            var e = t.$image;
                            i.isClosing || !t.isLoading || e && e.length && e[0].complete || t.hasError || i.showLoading(t)

                    },

                        if (s) {
                            i = t.devicePixelRatio || 1, a = t.innerWidth * i, (o = s.split(",").map(function(t) {
                                var e = {};

                                    var o = parseInt(t.substring(0, t.length - 1), 10);
                                    if (0 === n) return e.url = t;
                                    o && (e.value = o, e.postfix = t[t.length - 1])
                                }), e
                            })).sort(function(t, e) {
                                return t.value - e.value
                            });
                            for (var r = 0; r < o.length; r++) {
                                var c = o[r];
                                if ("w" === c.postfix && c.value >= a || "x" === c.postfix && c.value >= i) {
                                    n = c;
                                    break
                                }

                        }
                    },

                }), n.fancybox = {

                    },
                    open: function(t, e, n) {

                    },
                    close: function(t) {

                    },

                    },
                    isMobile: /Android|webOS|iPhone|iPad|iPod|BlackBerry|IEMobile|Opera Mini/i.test(navigator.userAgent),

                    }(),
                    getTranslate: function(t) {

                        }
                    },

                    },

        function HSVtoRGB(t, e, r) {
            var i, s, a, n, o, h, p, l;

        }

        function RGBtoHSV(t, e, r) {
            var i, s = Math.max(t, e, r),
                a = Math.min(t, e, r),
                n = s - a,
                o = 0 === s ? 0 : n / s,

                    break;
                case r:
                    i = t - e + 4 * n, i /= 6 * n
            }

        }

        BaseRenderer.prototype.checkLayers = function(t) {
            var e, r, i = this.layers.length;
            for (this.completeLayers = !0, e = i - 1; 0 <= e; e--) this.elements[e] || (r = this.layers[e]).ip - r.st <= t - this.layers[e].st && r.op - r.st > t - this.layers[e].st && this.buildItem(e), this.completeLayers = !!this.elements[e] && this.completeLayers;
            this.checkPendingElements()
        }, BaseRenderer.prototype.createItem = function(t) {
            switch (t.ty) {
                case 2:
                    return this.createImage(t);
                case 0:
                    return this.createComp(t);
                case 1:
                    return this.createSolid(t);
                case 3:
                    return this.createNull(t);
                case 4:
                    return this.createShape(t);
                case 5:
                    return this.createText(t);
                case 13:

                var i = e.style,
                    s = e.d;
                s && (s._mdf || r) && s.dashStr && (i.pElem.setAttribute("stroke-dasharray", s.dashStr), i.pElem.setAttribute("stroke-dashoffset", s.dashoffset[0])), e.c && (e.c._mdf || r) && i.pElem.setAttribute("stroke", "rgb(" + bm_floor(e.c.v[0]) + "," + bm_floor(e.c.v[1]) + "," + bm_floor(e.c.v[2]) + ")"), (e.o._mdf || r) && i.pElem.setAttribute("stroke-opacity", e.o.v), (e.w._mdf || r) && (i.pElem.setAttribute("stroke-width", e.w.v), i.msElem && i.msElem.setAttribute("stroke-width", e.w.v))
            }
            return {
                createRenderFunction: function(t) {
                    switch (t.ty, t.ty) {
                        case "fl":
                            return i;
                        case "gf":
                            return a;
                        case "gs":
                            return s;
                        case "st":
                            return n;
                        case "sh":
                        case "el":
                        case "rc":
                        case "sr":
                            return r;
                        case "tr":
                            return e
                    }
                }
            }

        ShapeTransformManager.prototype = {
            addTransformSequence: function(t) {
                var e, r = t.length,
                    i = "_";
                for (e = 0; e < r; e += 1) i += t[e].transform.key + "_";
                var s = this.sequences[i];
                return s || (s = {
                    transforms: [].concat(t),
                    finalTransform: new Matrix,
                    _mdf: !1
                }, this.sequences[i] = s, this.sequenceList.push(s)), s
            },
            processSequence: function(t, e) {
                for (var r, i = 0, s = t.transforms.length, a = e; i < s && !e;) {
                    if (t.transforms[i].transform.mProps._mdf) {
                        a = !0;
                        break
                    }
                    i += 1
                }
                if (a)
                    for (t.finalTransform.reset(), i = s - 1; 0 <= i; i -= 1) r = t.transforms[i].transform.mProps.v.props, t.finalTransform.transform(r[0], r[1], r[2], r[3], r[4], r[5], r[6], r[7], r[8], r[9], r[10], r[11], r[12], r[13], r[14], r[15]);
                t._mdf = a
            },
            processSequences: function(t) {
                var e, r = this.sequenceList.length;
                for (e = 0; e < r; e += 1) this.processSequence(this.sequenceList[e], t)
            },
            getNewKey: function() {
                return "_" + this.transform_key_count++
            }

        SVGMatte3Effect.prototype.findSymbol = function(t) {

            }

        }, SVGMatte3Effect.prototype.replaceInParent = function(t, e) {

            }

            }
        }, AnimationItem.prototype.adjustSegment = function(t, e) {

        }, AnimationItem.prototype.playSegments = function(t, e) {

        }, AnimationItem.prototype.destroy = function(t) {

        }, AnimationItem.prototype.getDuration = function(t) {

        }, AnimationItem.prototype.trigger = function(t) {
            if (this._cbs && this._cbs[t]) switch (t) {
                case "enterFrame":
                    this.triggerEvent(t, new BMEnterFrameEvent(t, this.currentFrame, this.totalFrames, this.frameModifier));
                    break;
                case "loopComplete":
                    this.triggerEvent(t, new BMCompleteLoopEvent(t, this.loop, this.playCount, this.frameMult));
                    break;
                case "complete":
                    this.triggerEvent(t, new BMCompleteEvent(t, this.frameMult));
                    break;
                case "segmentStart":
                    this.triggerEvent(t, new BMSegmentStartEvent(t, this.firstFrame, this.totalFrames));
                    break;
                case "destroy":
                    this.triggerEvent(t, new BMDestroyEvent(t, this));
                    break;
                default:
                    this.triggerEvent(t)
            }
            "enterFrame" === t && this.onEnterFrame && this.onEnterFrame.call(this, new BMEnterFrameEvent(t, this.currentFrame, this.totalFrames, this.frameMult)), "loopComplete" === t && this.onLoopComplete && this.onLoopComplete.call(this, new BMCompleteLoopEvent(t, this.loop, this.playCount, this.frameMult)), "complete" === t && this.onComplete && this.onComplete.call(this, new BMCompleteEvent(t, this.frameMult)), "segmentStart" === t && this.onSegmentStart && this.onSegmentStart.call(this, new BMSegmentStartEvent(t, this.firstFrame, this.totalFrames)), "destroy" === t && this.onDestroy && this.onDestroy.call(this, new BMDestroyEvent(t, this))

        var Expressions = (EO = {}, EO.initExpressions = function(t) {
                var e = 0,
                    r = [];
                t.renderer.compInterface = CompExpressionInterface(t.renderer), t.renderer.globalData.projectInterface.registerComposition(t.renderer), t.renderer.globalData.pushExpression = function() {
                    e += 1
                }, t.renderer.globalData.popExpression = function() {
                    0 == (e -= 1) && function() {
                        var t, e = r.length;
                        for (t = 0; t < e; t += 1) r[t].release();
                        r.length = 0
                    }()
                }, t.renderer.globalData.registerExpressionProperty = function(t) {
                    -1 === r.indexOf(t) && r.push(t)
                }
            }, EO),

        expressionsPlugin = Expressions;
        var ExpressionManager = function() {
                var ob = {},
                    Math = BMMath,
                    window = null,
                    document = null;

                function $bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) {
                    return t.constructor === Array || t.constructor === Float32Array
                }

                function isNumerable(t, e) {
                    return "number" === t || "boolean" === t || "string" === t || e instanceof Number
                }

                function $bm_neg(t) {
                    var e = typeof t;
                    if ("number" == e || "boolean" == e || t instanceof Number) return -t;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t)) {
                        var r, i = t.length,
                            s = [];
                        for (r = 0; r < i; r += 1) s[r] = -t[r];
                        return s
                    }
                    return t.propType ? t.v : void 0
                }
                var easeInBez = BezierFactory.getBezierEasing(.333, 0, .833, .833, "easeIn").get,
                    easeOutBez = BezierFactory.getBezierEasing(.167, .167, .667, 1, "easeOut").get,
                    easeInOutBez = BezierFactory.getBezierEasing(.33, 0, .667, 1, "easeInOut").get;

                function sum(t, e) {
                    var r = typeof t,
                        i = typeof e;
                    if ("string" == r || "string" == i) return t + e;
                    if (isNumerable(r, t) && isNumerable(i, e)) return t + e;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) && isNumerable(i, e)) return (t = t.slice(0))[0] = t[0] + e, t;
                    if (isNumerable(r, t) && $bm_isInstanceOfArray(e)) return (e = e.slice(0))[0] = t + e[0], e;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) && $bm_isInstanceOfArray(e)) {
                        for (var s = 0, a = t.length, n = e.length, o = []; s < a || s < n;)("number" == typeof t[s] || t[s] instanceof Number) && ("number" == typeof e[s] || e[s] instanceof Number) ? o[s] = t[s] + e[s] : o[s] = void 0 === e[s] ? t[s] : t[s] || e[s], s += 1;
                        return o
                    }
                    return 0
                }
                var add = sum;

                function sub(t, e) {
                    var r = typeof t,
                        i = typeof e;
                    if (isNumerable(r, t) && isNumerable(i, e)) return "string" == r && (t = parseInt(t)), "string" == i && (e = parseInt(e)), t - e;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) && isNumerable(i, e)) return (t = t.slice(0))[0] = t[0] - e, t;
                    if (isNumerable(r, t) && $bm_isInstanceOfArray(e)) return (e = e.slice(0))[0] = t - e[0], e;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) && $bm_isInstanceOfArray(e)) {
                        for (var s = 0, a = t.length, n = e.length, o = []; s < a || s < n;)("number" == typeof t[s] || t[s] instanceof Number) && ("number" == typeof e[s] || e[s] instanceof Number) ? o[s] = t[s] - e[s] : o[s] = void 0 === e[s] ? t[s] : t[s] || e[s], s += 1;
                        return o
                    }
                    return 0
                }

                function mul(t, e) {
                    var r, i, s, a = typeof t,
                        n = typeof e;
                    if (isNumerable(a, t) && isNumerable(n, e)) return t * e;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) && isNumerable(n, e)) {
                        for (s = t.length, r = createTypedArray("float32", s), i = 0; i < s; i += 1) r[i] = t[i] * e;
                        return r
                    }
                    if (isNumerable(a, t) && $bm_isInstanceOfArray(e)) {
                        for (s = e.length, r = createTypedArray("float32", s), i = 0; i < s; i += 1) r[i] = t * e[i];
                        return r
                    }
                    return 0
                }

                function div(t, e) {
                    var r, i, s, a = typeof t,
                        n = typeof e;
                    if (isNumerable(a, t) && isNumerable(n, e)) return t / e;
                    if ($bm_isInstanceOfArray(t) && isNumerable(n, e)) {
                        for (s = t.length, r = createTypedArray("float32", s), i = 0; i < s; i += 1) r[i] = t[i] / e;
                        return r
                    }
                    if (isNumerable(a, t) && $bm_isInstanceOfArray(e)) {
                        for (s = e.length, r = createTypedArray("float32", s), i = 0; i < s; i += 1) r[i] = t / e[i];
                        return r
                    }
                    return 0
                }

                function mod(t, e) {
                    return "string" == typeof t && (t = parseInt(t)), "string" == typeof e && (e = parseInt(e)), t % e
                }
                var $bm_sum = sum,
                    $bm_sub = sub,
                    $bm_mul = mul,

                    $bm_mod = mod;

                function clamp(t, e, r) {
                    if (r < e) {
                        var i = r;
                        r = e, e = i
                    }
                    return Math.min(Math.max(t, e), r)
                }

                function radiansToDegrees(t) {
                    return t / degToRads
                }
                var radians_to_degrees = radiansToDegrees;

                function degreesToRadians(t) {
                    return t * degToRads
                }
                var degrees_to_radians = radiansToDegrees,
                    helperLengthArray = [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0];

                function length(t, e) {
                    if ("number" == typeof t || t instanceof Number) return e = e || 0, Math.abs(t - e);
                    e || (e = helperLengthArray);
                    var r, i = Math.min(t.length, e.length),
                        s = 0;
                    for (r = 0; r < i; r += 1) s += Math.pow(e[r] - t[r], 2);
                    return Math.sqrt(s)
                }

                function normalize(t) {
                    return div(t, length(t))
                }

                function rgbToHsl(t) {
                    var e, r, i = t[0],
                        s = t[1],
                        a = t[2],
                        n = Math.max(i, s, a),
                        o = Math.min(i, s, a),
                        h = (n + o) / 2;
                    if (n == o) e = r = 0;
                    else {
                        var p = n - o;
                        switch (r = .5 < h ? p / (2 - n - o) : p / (n + o), n) {
                            case i:
                                e = (s - a) / p + (s < a ? 6 : 0);
                                break;
                            case s:
                                e = (a - i) / p + 2;
                                break;
                            case a:
                                e = (i - s) / p + 4
                        }
                        e /= 6
                    }
                    return [e, r, h, t[3]]
                }

                function hue2rgb(t, e, r) {
                    return r < 0 && (r += 1), 1 < r && (r -= 1), r < 1 / 6 ? t + 6 * (e - t) * r : r < .5 ? e : r < 2 / 3 ? t + (e - t) * (2 / 3 - r) * 6 : t
                }

                function hslToRgb(t) {
                    var e, r, i, s = t[0],
                        a = t[1],
                        n = t[2];
                    if (0 === a) e = r = i = n;
                    else {
                        var o = n < .5 ? n * (1 + a) : n + a - n * a,
                            h = 2 * n - o;
                        e = hue2rgb(h, o, s + 1 / 3), r = hue2rgb(h, o, s), i = hue2rgb(h, o, s - 1 / 3)
                    }
                    return [e, r, i, t[3]]
                }

                function linear(t, e, r, i, s) {
                    if (void 0 !== i && void 0 !== s || (i = e, s = r, e = 0, r = 1), r < e) {
                        var a = r;
                        r = e, e = a
                    }
                    if (t <= e) return i;
                    if (r <= t) return s;
                    var n = r === e ? 0 : (t - e) / (r - e);
                    if (!i.length) return i + (s - i) * n;
                    var o, h = i.length,
                        p = createTypedArray("float32", h);
                    for (o = 0; o < h; o += 1) p[o] = i[o] + (s[o] - i[o]) * n;
                    return p
                }

                function random(t, e) {
                    if (void 0 === e && (void 0 === t ? (t = 0, e = 1) : (e = t, t = void 0)), e.length) {
                        var r, i = e.length;
                        t || (t = createTypedArray("float32", i));
                        var s = createTypedArray("float32", i),
                            a = BMMath.random();
                        for (r = 0; r < i; r += 1) s[r] = t[r] + a * (e[r] - t[r]);
                        return s
                    }
                    return void 0 === t && (t = 0), t + BMMath.random() * (e - t)
                }

                function createPath(t, e, r, i) {

                    return n
                }

                    function applyEase(t, e, r, i, s, a) {

                    }

                    function nearestKey(t) {

                duration: 1500,
                delay: 800 + 200 * index,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            })
        }), anime({
            targets: this.bottomLine,
            scaleX: 1.001,
            duration: 1500,
            delay: 1400,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        })
    }, AnimateExptzBlc.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.AnimateExptzBlc = AnimateExptzBlc
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function AnimateFooter(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.init()
    }
    AnimateFooter.prototype.init = function() {
        this.heading = this.el.find("h2").get(), this.bottom = this.el.find(".footer__company p, .footer__company a").get(), this.bg = this.el.find(".bg")[0], this.list = this.el.find(".footer-links li").get(), this.social = this.el.find(".footer__social").css("overflow", "hidden"), this.icons = this.el.find(".footer__social li").get(), this.footerlinkCache = [], this.el.find(".footer-links-blc__col").each(function(index, el) {
            var item = {},
                $el = $(el);
            item.line = $el.find(".line").get(), item.split = [];
            var $text = $el.find("h2, a");
            anime.set(item.line, {
                scaleX: 0,
                transformOrigin: "left center",
                opacity: 0
            }), $text.each(function(index, el) {
                var split = Splitting({
                    target: el,
                    by: "lines"
                });
                app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), item.split.push(split[0].lines)
            }), this.footerlinkCache.push(item)
        }.bind(this)), anime.set(this.bottom, {
            translateY: "100%",
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(this.heading.concat(this.list), {
            translateY: 0
        }), anime.set(this.icons, {
            translateY: "100%",
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(this.bg, {
            scaleY: "0",
            transformOrigin: "center top"
        })
    }, AnimateFooter.prototype.reveal = function() {
        anime({
            targets: this.bg,
            scaleY: 1,
            duration: 3e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), this.footerlinkCache.forEach(function(item) {
            anime({
                targets: item.line,
                scaleX: 1.001,
                opacity: [1, 1],
                duration: app.animationDuration,
                delay: 1700,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), item.split.reduce(function(accumulator, line) {
                return accumulator.concat(line)
            }, []).forEach(function(line, index) {
                anime({
                    targets: line,
                    translateY: ["100%", 0],
                    opacity: [1, 1],
                    duration: app.animationDuration,
                    easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
                    delay: 1100 + index * app.animationStagger
                })
            })
        }), anime({
            targets: this.bottom,
            translateY: [100, 0],
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: 2e3
            }),
            opacity: 1,
            duration: app.animationDuration,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.icons,
            translateY: [100, 0],
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: 2e3
            }),
            opacity: 1,
            duration: app.animationDuration,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)"
        }), setTimeout(function() {
            this.social = this.el.find(".footer__social").css("overflow", "")
        }.bind(this), 2e3)
    }, AnimateFooter.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.AnimateFooter = AnimateFooter
}();

    function AnimateFooterNewsletter(el) {

! function() {
    function FormAnimation(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.$el = $(el), this.vars = {
            type: this.setType(this.$el)
        }, this.init()
    }
    FormAnimation.prototype.init = function() {
        switch (this.vars.type) {
            case "text":
                this.setDefaultStyleText(this.$el);
                break;
            case "radio":
                this.setDefaultStyleRadio(this.$el);
                break;
            case "range":
                this.setDefaultStyleRange(this.$el)
        }
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.reveal = function(delay) {
        switch (this.vars.type) {
            case "text":
                this.animateText(delay);
                break;
            case "radio":
                this.animateRadio(delay);
                break;
            case "range":
                this.animateRange(delay)
        }
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.setDefaultStyleText = function(el) {
        this.vars.line = el.find(".line"), this.vars.text = el.find("label, .upload-button, .icon, .chosen-single, input"), anime.set(this.vars.text.get(), {
            opacity: 0,
            translateY: 100
        }), anime.set(this.vars.line.get(), {
            transformOrigin: "left center",
            scaleX: 0
        })
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.setDefaultStyleRadio = function(el) {
        this.vars.line = el.find(".line"), this.vars.text = el.find("label"), anime.set(this.vars.text.get(), {
            opacity: 0,
            translateY: 100
        }), anime.set(this.vars.line.get(), {
            transformOrigin: "left center",
            scaleX: 0
        })
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.setDefaultStyleRange = function(el) {
        this.vars.line = el.find(".rangeslider--horizontal"), this.vars.knob = el.find(".rangeslider__handle"), this.vars.text = el.find("label, .range-current, .range-min, .range-max"), anime.set(this.vars.text.get(), {
            opacity: 0,
            translateY: 100
        }), anime.set(this.vars.line.get(), {
            scaleX: .7,
            transformOrigin: "left center"
        }), anime.set(this.vars.knob.get(), {
            scale: 0,
            translateX: "-" + this.vars.knob.css("left")
        })
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.animateText = function(delay) {
        anime({
            targets: this.vars.text.get(),
            translateY: [100, 0],
            opacity: [0, 1],
            duration: app.animationDuration,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: delay
            })
        }), anime({
            targets: this.vars.line.get(),
            scaleX: [0, 1],
            duration: app.animationDuration - 300,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: delay + 700,
            complete: function() {
                this.vars.line.css({
                    transform: "",
                    transformOrigin: ""
                })
            }.bind(this)
        })
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.animateRange = function(delay) {
        anime({
            targets: this.vars.text.get(),
            translateY: [100, 0],
            opacity: [0, 1],
            duration: app.animationDuration,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: delay
            })
        }), anime({
            targets: this.vars.line.get(),
            scaleX: 1,
            duration: app.animationDuration - 300,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: delay + 300
        }), anime({
            targets: this.vars.knob.get(),
            translateX: 0,
            duration: app.animationDuration - 300,
            scale: {
                value: 1,
                duration: 300
            },
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: delay + 500
        })
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.animateRadio = function(delay) {
        anime({
            targets: this.vars.text.get(),
            translateY: [100, 0],
            opacity: [0, 1],
            duration: app.animationDuration,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: delay
            })
        })
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.setType = function(el) {
        return el.hasClass("form-field--range") ? "range" : el.hasClass("form-field--radio") ? "radio" : "text"
    }, FormAnimation.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "setType", "setDefaultStyleText", "reveal"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.AnimateFormField = FormAnimation
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function AnimateGroup(el) {
        switch (this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.inViewEvents = [], this.lottieAnimations = [], this.animationType = this.el.data("animate"), this.animationType) {
            case "block":
                this.animateText();
                break;
            case "dsc-block":
                this.animateDsc();
                break;
            case "footer":
                this.animateFooter();
                break;
            case "footer-newsletter":
                this.animateFooterNewsletter();
                break;
            case "chinese-footer":
                this.animateChineseFooter();
                break;
            case "head":
                this.animateHead();
                break;
            case "hero":
                this.animateHero();
                break;
            case "chat-blc":
                this.animateChatBlc();
                break;
            case "location":
                this.animateLocationBlc();
                break;
            case "num-block":
                this.animateNumBlc();
                break;
            case "news-list":
                this.animateNewsList();
                break;
            case "video":
                this.animateVideo();
                break;
            case "form":
                this.animateForm();
                break;
            case "testimony":
                this.animateTestimony();
                break;
            default:
                this.animateGeneric()
        }
    }
    AnimateGroup.prototype.animateGeneric = function() {
        var elements = this.el.find("[data-animate-el]");
        elements.css("opacity", 0), elements.each(function(index, el) {
            var outerWrapper = $("<span />", {
                    class: "--anim-out",
                    css: {
                        overflow: "hidden",
                        display: "inline-block",
                        verticalAlign: "bottom"
                    }
                }),
                innerWrapper = $("<span />", {
                    class: "--anim-in",
                    css: {
                        display: "inline-block",
                        verticalAlign: "bottom"
                    }
                });
            $(el).wrapInner(innerWrapper), $(el).wrapInner(outerWrapper), anime.set(innerWrapper[0], {
                translateY: "100%"
            })
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), elements.css("opacity", 1), anime({
                targets: elements.find(".--anim-in").get(),
                translateY: ["100%", 0],
                duration: 2e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger)
            }))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateText = function() {
        var that = this,
            heading = this.el.find("[data-animate-heading], blockquote, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6").filter(":not([data-animate-text])"),
            text = this.el.find("[data-animate-text], p, label").filter(":not([data-animate-number]), :not([data-animate-heading])").filter(function(index, item) {
                return 0 === $(item).closest("ul, ol").length
            }),
            line = this.el.find(".line").filter(function(index, el) {
                return 0 === $(el).closest("li").length
            }),
            numbers = this.el.find("[data-animate-number]"),
            images = this.el.find("[data-animate-image]"),
            list = (this.el.data("animate-offset"), this.el.find("ul, ol")),
            link = this.el.find(".link");
        this.el.css("opacity", 0).addClass("toAnimate"), this.inViewEvents.push(InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), that.el.css("opacity", 1).removeClass("toAnimate"))
        })), line.each(function(index, el) {
            var meta = {
                    el: el,
                    delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
                },
                inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), that.handleDrawLine(meta))
                });
            $(el).css("transformOrigin", "left center"), that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        }), heading.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            });
            var meta = {
                    split: split,
                    el: el,
                    delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
                },
                inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), anime.set(el, {
                        opacity: 1
                    }), that.handleHeadingCutInview(meta))
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        }), numbers.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines);
            var meta = {
                    split: split,
                    el: el,
                    delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
                },
                inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), that.handleNumbersInview(meta))
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            var meta = {
                el: el,
                delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
            };
            anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            });
            var inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                inview && (this.destroy(), that.handleTextInview(meta))
            });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        }), list.each(function(index, el) {
            $(el).addClass("hide-line").children().css("opacity", 0);
            var meta = {
                    el: el.children,
                    delay: 300
                },
                inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), that.handlelistInview(meta))
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        }), link.each(function(index, el) {
            var $el = $(el);
            $el.css({
                opacity: 0
            }), anime.set($el.find(".line")[0], {
                transformOrigin: "left center",
                scaleX: 0
            });
            var meta = {
                    el: el,
                    text: $el.find(".text")[0],
                    line: $el.find(".line")[0],
                    delay: $el.data("animate-delay") || 0
                },
                inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), that.handleLinkInview(meta))
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        }), images.each(function(index, el) {
            anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            });
            var delay = $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0,
                inviewInstance = InView(el, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), anime({
                        targets: el,
                        translateY: [100, 0],
                        opacity: [1, 1],
                        duration: app.animationDuration,
                        easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
                        delay: parseInt(delay)
                    }))
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateVideo = function() {
        var rect = this.el.find(".icon")[0],
            icon = this.el.find("svg path")[0],
            image = this.el.find("[data-animate-image]")[0];
        anime.set(image, {
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(icon, {
            scale: 0,
            translateY: "300px"
        }), anime.set(rect, {
            scale: 0,
            translateY: "300px"
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(image, function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: image,
                clipPath: ["inset(100% 0% 0% 0%)", "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)"],
                scale: [2, 1],
                opacity: [1, 1],
                duration: 2e3,
                easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)"
            }), anime({
                targets: [icon, rect],
                scale: [0, 1],
                translateY: ["300px", 0],
                duration: 2e3,
                easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)"
            }))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateDsc = function() {
        var that = this,
            heading = this.el.find("[data-animate-heading], h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6").filter(":not([data-animate-text])"),
            text = this.el.find("[data-animate-text], p, label").filter(":not([data-animate-number]), :not([data-animate-heading])"),
            link = this.el.find(".link"),
            textMeta = [],
            linkMeta = [],
            headingMeta = [];
        this.el.css("opacity", 0).addClass("toAnimate"), heading.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), headingMeta.push({
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
            })
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            textMeta.push({
                el: el,
                delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 300
            })
        }), link.each(function(index, el) {
            var $el = $(el);
            $el.css({
                opacity: 0
            }), anime.set($el.find(".line")[0], {
                transformOrigin: "left center",
                scaleX: 0
            }), linkMeta.push({
                el: el,
                text: $el.find(".text")[0],
                line: $el.find(".line")[0],
                delay: $el.data("animate-delay") || 0
            })
        }), this.inViewEvents.push(InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), that.el.css("opacity", 1).removeClass("toAnimate"), headingMeta.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleHeadingCutInview(meta)
            }), textMeta.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleTextInview(meta)
            }), setTimeout(function() {
                linkMeta.forEach(function(meta) {
                    that.handleLinkInview(meta)
                })
            }, 300))
        }))
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateHero = function() {
        var that = this,
            text = this.el.find(".desc-small p, .memo p, .count, .helper"),
            heading = this.el.find("h1, h2, .desc p, p.desc"),
            line = this.el.find(".line"),
            meta = {
                text: [],
                line: [],
                heading: []
            };
        line.each(function(index, el) {
            meta.line.push({
                el: el,
                delay: 800
            }), $(el).css("transformOrigin", "left center")
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            }), meta.text.push({
                split: el,
                el: el,
                delay: 150
            })
        }), heading.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), meta.heading.push({
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: 200 * index
            })
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), meta.line.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleDrawLine(meta)
            }), meta.text.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleTextInview(meta)
            }), meta.heading.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleHeadingCutInview(meta)
            }))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateHead = function() {
        var that = this,
            list = this.el.find("li"),
            text = this.el.find("p").filter(function(index, item) {
                return 0 === $(item).closest("ul, ol, .gen-blc__header__cont").length
            }),
            heading = this.el.find("h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6").filter(function(index, item) {
                return 0 === $(item).closest("ul, ol, .gen-blc__header__cont").length
            }),
            item = this.el.find("[data-aniamte-item]"),
            topText = this.el.find(".gen-blc__header__cont h2, .gen-blc__header__cont p"),
            line = this.el.find(".line"),
            meta = {
                text: [],
                line: [],
                list: [],
                topText: [],
                heading: []
            };
        list.addClass("hide-line"), anime.set(list.get(), {
            opacity: 0
        }), meta.list = {
            el: list.get(),
            delay: 300
        }, line.each(function(index, el) {
            meta.line.push({
                el: el,
                delay: 800
            }), $(el).css("transformOrigin", "left center")
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            }), meta.text.push({
                split: el,
                el: el,
                delay: 0
            })
        }), item.css("opacity", 0), topText.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), meta.topText.push({
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: 200 * index
            })
        }), heading.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), meta.heading.push({
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: 200 * index
            })
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), meta.line.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleDrawLine(meta)
            }), meta.text.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleTextInview(meta)
            }), meta.heading.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleHeadingCutInview(meta)
            }), meta.topText.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleHeadingCutInview(meta)
            }), anime({
                targets: item.get(),
                translateY: [600, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                duration: app.animationDuration,
                easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)"
            }), that.handlelistInview(meta.list))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateTestimony = function() {
        var that = this,
            text = this.el.find(".testimony-blc__cont, .testimony-blc__cont"),
            bodyContent = this.el.find("blockquote, .testimony-blc__body p"),
            line = this.el.find(".line"),
            meta = {
                text: [],
                line: []
            },
            bg = this.el.find(".testimony-blc__bg");
        anime.set(that.el.get(), {
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(bg.get(), {
            scaleY: 0,
            transformOrigin: "center bottom"
        }), line.each(function(index, el) {
            anime.set(el, {
                scaleX: 0
            }), meta.line.push({
                el: el,
                delay: 400
            }), $(el).css("transformOrigin", "left center")
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            }), meta.text.push({
                el: el,
                delay: 100 * index
            })
        }), bodyContent.each(function(index, el) {
            anime.set(el, {
                opacity: 0
            }), meta.text.push({
                el: el,
                delay: 100 * index + 300
            })
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: bg.get(),
                scaleY: 1,
                duration: app.animationDuration,
                easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)"
            }), meta.line.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleDrawLine(meta)
            }), meta.text.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleTextInview(meta)
            }), anime.set(that.el.get(), {
                opacity: 1
            }))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateForm = function() {
        var that = this,
            text = this.el.find("h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p"),
            formFields = this.el.find(".form-field"),
            formFieldInstances = [],
            meta = {
                text: [],
                line: [],
                list: []
            };
        formFields.each(function(index, el) {
            formFieldInstances.push(new app.AnimateFormField(el))
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), meta.text.push({
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: 60 * index
            })
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), meta.text.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleHeadingInview(meta)
            }), formFieldInstances.forEach(function(ff, index) {
                ff.reveal(100 * index)
            }))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateNewsList = function() {
        var that = this;
        this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__slide").each(function(index, item) {
            var instance = new app.AnimateNewsItem($(item), !0),
                inviewInstance = InView(item, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateChineseFooter = function() {
        var that = this;
        this.el.each(function(index, item) {
            var instance = new app.AnimateChineseFooter($(item)),
                inviewInstance = InView(item, function(inview) {
                    inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
                });
            that.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateChatBlc = function() {
        var instance = new app.AnimateChatBlc(this.el),
            inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
                inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
            });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateLocationBlc = function() {
        var instance = new app.AnimateLocationBlc(this.el),
            inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
                inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
            });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateFooter = function() {
        var instance = new app.AnimateFooter(this.el),
            inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
                inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
            });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateFooterNewsletter = function() {
        var instance = new app.AnimateFooterNewsletter(this.el),
            inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
                inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
            });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.animateNumBlc = function() {
        var that = this,
            text = this.el.find("h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p"),
            list = this.el.find("li"),
            line = this.el.find(".line"),
            numbers = this.el.find("[data-animate-number]"),
            meta = {
                text: [],
                line: [],
                list: []
            };
        list.append($("<span/>", {
            class: "line"
        })), line.each(function(index, el) {
            meta.line.push({
                el: el,
                delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
            }), $(el).css("transformOrigin", "left center")
        }), text.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), meta.text.push({
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: 60 * index
            })
        }), meta.list = {
            el: list.get(),
            delay: 300
        }, numbers.each(function(index, el) {
            var split = Splitting({
                target: el,
                by: "lines"
            });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines, !0), meta.num = {
                split: split,
                el: el,
                delay: $(el).data("animate-delay") || 0
            }
        });
        var inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
            inview && (this.destroy(), meta.line.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleDrawLine(meta)
            }), meta.text.forEach(function(meta) {
                that.handleHeadingCutInview(meta)
            }), that.handleNumbersInview(meta.num), that.handlelistInview(meta.list))
        });
        this.inViewEvents.push(inviewInstance)
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handleHeadingInview = function(meta) {
        $(meta.el).removeClass("toAnimate"), meta.split[0].lines.forEach(function(line, index) {
            anime({
                targets: line,
                translateY: [300 + 100 * index, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                duration: app.animationDuration,
                easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
                delay: meta.delay + 50 * index
            })
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handleHeadingCutInview = function(meta) {
        $(meta.el).removeClass("toAnimate"), meta.split.forEach(function(heading) {
            heading.lines.forEach(function(line, index) {
                anime({
                    targets: line,
                    translateY: ["100%", 0],
                    opacity: [1, 1],
                    duration: app.animationDuration,
                    easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
                    delay: meta.delay + index * app.animationStagger
                })
            })
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handleLinkInview = function(meta) {
        meta.el.style.opacity = "", meta.text.style.display = "inline-block";
        var wrap = $("<span/>", {
            css: {
                display: "inline-block",
                overflow: "hidden",
                verticalAlign: "bottom"
            }
        });
        $(meta.text).wrap(wrap), anime({
            targets: meta.text,
            translateY: ["50px", 0],
            opacity: [0, 1],
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            complete: function() {
                meta.text.style.display = ""
            }
        }), this.handleDrawLine({
            el: meta.line,
            delay: 300
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handleNumbersInview = function(meta) {
        $(meta.el).css("opacity", "").removeClass("toAnimate"), meta.split[0].lines.forEach(function(line, index) {
            anime({
                targets: line,
                translateY: ["100%", 0],
                duration: 2e3,
                easing: "easeInOutCirc",
                delay: meta.delay + 100 * index
            });
            var obj = {
                val: 0
            };
            anime({
                targets: obj,
                val: parseInt($(line).text()),
                easing: "easeOutQuad",
                duration: 4e3,
                round: 1,
                update: function() {
                    $(line).html(obj.val.toString().padStart(2, 0))
                }
            })
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handleTextInview = function(meta) {
        $(meta.el).removeClass("toAnimate"), anime({
            targets: meta.el,
            translateY: ["100", 0],
            opacity: [0, 1],
            duration: app.animationDuration,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: meta.delay
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handlelistInview = function(meta) {
        $(meta.el).each(function(index, item) {
            anime({
                targets: item,
                translateY: [100, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                duration: app.animationDuration,
                easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
                delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                    start: meta.delay
                })
            }), setTimeout(function() {
                $(item).removeClass("hide-line")
            }, 60 * index + 800)
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.handleDrawLine = function(meta) {
        anime({
            targets: meta.el,
            scaleX: [0, 1.001],
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "cubicBezier(0.25, 0.1, 0.24, 1.01)",
            delay: meta.delay,
            complete: function() {
                $(meta.el).css("transformOrigin", "")
            }
        })
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.inViewEvents.forEach(function(item) {
            item.destroy()
        }.bind(this))
    }, AnimateGroup.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["destroy", "handleHeadingInview", "handleTextInview", "handleDrawLine", "handleLinkInview", "animateGeneric", "animateHero", "animateHead", "animateLocationBlc"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.AnimateGroup = AnimateGroup
}();
var app = app || {};

            return $(listItem).find("li").addClass("hide-line").get()
        }), anime.set(this.headerText, {
            translateY: "400px",
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(this.headerLine, {
            scaleX: 0,
            transformOrigin: "left center"
        })

            targets: this.headerLine,

        })
    }, AnimateHead.prototype.createBounds = function() {

        ["init"].forEach(function(fn) {

    function() {
        function AnimateIcon(el) {
            this.createBounds(), this.el = el, eval(this.el.find("script").html()), this.lottieData = window[this.el.data("icon-animate")], this.svg = this.el.find("svg"), this.value = this.el.data("val"), this.valueAlt = this.el.data("val-alt"), this.toChange = !!this.valueAlt, this.numEl = this.el.next(".count").find(".word"), this.toChangeTimer = null, this.playing = !1, this.init()
        }
        AnimateIcon.prototype.init = function() {
            this.svg.hide(), this.player = lottie.loadAnimation({
                container: this.el[0],
                renderer: "svg",
                loop: !1,
                autoplay: !1,
                animationData: this.lottieData,
                rendererSettings: {
                    className: "lottie-icon-animation"
                }
            }), this.player.setSpeed(.6), this.player.addEventListener("DOMLoaded", function() {
                this.el.find(".lottie-icon-animation").css({
                    width: "",
                    height: ""
                })
            }.bind(this)), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(inview) {
                var that = this;
                inview ? this.playing || (this.playing = !0, this.player.goToAndPlay(0), this.toChange && (this.numEl.html(this.value), this.toChangeTimer = setTimeout(function() {
                    var obj = {
                        val: parseInt(that.value)
                    };
                    anime({
                        targets: obj,
                        val: parseInt(that.valueAlt),
                        easing: "easeOutQuad",
                        duration: 1e3,
                        round: 1,
                        update: function() {
                            that.numEl.html(obj.val.toString().padStart(2, 0))
                        }
                    })
                }, 5e3))) : this.playing && (this.playing = !1, this.player.stop(0), this.toChangeTimer && clearTimeout(this.toChangeTimer))
            }.bind(this))
        }, AnimateIcon.prototype.destroy = function() {
            this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.player.destroy()
        }, AnimateIcon.prototype.createBounds = function() {
            var that = this;
            ["init", "destroy"].forEach(function(fn) {
                that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
            })
        }, app.AnimateIcon = AnimateIcon
    }();

! function() {
    function AnimateNewsItem(el, fromBottom) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.fromBottom = fromBottom || !1, this.init()
    }
    AnimateNewsItem.prototype.init = function() {
        this.image = this.el.find(".bg-image")[0], this.imageParent = this.el.find(".link")[0], this.topText = this.el.find(".type").get(), this.body = this.el.find(".body").get(), anime.set(this.el[0], {
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(this.image, {
            scale: 2
        }), anime.set(this.imageParent, {
            clipPath: "inset(100% 0 0 0)"
        }), anime.set(this.topText, {
            translateY: "400px",
            display: "block"
        }), anime.set(this.body, {
            translateY: "400px",
            display: "block"
        })
    }, AnimateNewsItem.prototype.reveal = function() {
        this.fromBottom ? anime({
            targets: this.el[0],
            opacity: 1,
            translateY: {
                value: ["100%", 0],
                duration: 2e3
            },
            duration: 1500,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }) : anime({
            targets: this.el[0],
            opacity: 1,
            duration: 1500,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.imageParent,
            clipPath: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
            duration: 1500,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.image,
            scale: 1,
            duration: 1800,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), this.topText.forEach(function(item, index) {
            anime({
                targets: item,
                translateY: [400 + 300 * index, 0],
                duration: 1500,
                delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger),
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            })
        }), anime({
            targets: this.body,
            translateY: [400, 0],
            duration: 1500,
            delay: 300,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        })
    }, AnimateNewsItem.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.AnimateNewsItem = AnimateNewsItem
}(), app.BarbaTransition = Barba.BaseTransition.extend({
    start: function() {
        window.menu.isOpen ? (window.menu.closeMenu(), window.menu.el.one("menu-closed", function() {
            Promise.all([this.newContainerLoading]).then(this.fadeIn.bind(this))
        }.bind(this))) : Promise.all([this.newContainerLoading]).then(this.fadeIn.bind(this))
    },
    fadeIn: function() {
        var _this = this,
            $newContainer = $(this.newContainer),
            $oldContainer = $(this.oldContainer),
            bodyClasses = document.body.className,
            newClasses = -1 < bodyClasses.indexOf("custom-cursor") ? " custom-cursor " : "";
        newClasses += -1 < bodyClasses.indexOf("js-init") ? " js-init" : "", document.body.className = this.newContainer.getAttribute("data-class") + newClasses;
        var barbaEl = window.BarbaData.el,
            barbafrom = window.BarbaData.from; - 1 < "work-list next-project home-carousel".indexOf(barbafrom) ? ($newContainer.css("opacity", 0), $("html").css("scroll-behavior", "auto"), $("html, body").scrollTop(0), $("html").css("scroll-behavior", "")) : ($newContainer.animate({
            opacity: 0
        }, 0), $oldContainer.animate({
            opacity: 0
        }, 200, function() {
            $("html").css("scroll-behavior", "auto"), $("html, body").scrollTop(0), $("html").css("scroll-behavior", "")
        })), "work-list" === barbafrom ? (anime({
            targets: barbaEl.find(".glide__overlay").get(),
            opacity: .4,
            duration: 600,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint",
            complete: function() {
                $newContainer.css("opacity", 1), _this.done()
            }
        }), anime({
            targets: barbaEl.get(),
            height: window.outerWidth < app.MD_BREAKPOINT ? window.innerHeight : 667,
            duration: 800,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        })) : "next-project" === barbafrom || "home-carousel" === barbafrom ? (_this.done(), $newContainer.css("opacity", 1)) : (setTimeout(function() {
            $newContainer.animate({
                opacity: 1
            }, 300)
        }, 100), setTimeout(function() {
            _this.done()
        }, 200))
    }
});
