! function() {
    function Carousel(el, skipImageAnimation, skipAllAnimation) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.playImageAnimation = !skipImageAnimation, this.playAllAnimation = !skipAllAnimation, this.alt = this.el.hasClass("carousel--alt"), this.cache = [], this.imageSlider = this.el.find(".carousel__imgs-slider"), this.imagesContiner = this.el.find(".carousel__imgs"), this.pagination = this.el.find(".carousel__pagination"), this.slides = this.imageSlider.find(".carousel__imgs-slide"), this.slideImages = this.slides.find(".img").get(), this.textContainer = this.el.find(".carousel__text"), this.textSlideItems = this.textContainer.find(".carousel__text__item"), this.button = this.el.find(".carousel__button"), this.animation = null, this.current = 0, this.slidesLength = this.slides.length, this.images = this.slides.find(".img"), this.init(), this.resize()
    }
    Carousel.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized"), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.button.on("hold", function() {
            window.BarbaData = {
                el: null,
                from: "home-carousel"
            }, this.el.addClass("carousel--shift"), $("html, body").scrollTop(0), anime({
                targets: this.el.nextAll().get(),
                opacity: 0,
                translateY: "100%",
                easing: "easeInQuint",
                duration: 300
            })
        }.bind(this)), 1 < this.slidesLength ? this.imageSlider.owlCarousel({
            loop: !1,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            items: 1,
            onInitialized: function() {
                this.pagination.append(app.getSliderPagination("0" + this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.hammertime = new Hammer(this.el[0]), this.hammertime.on("pan", function(ev) {
                    ev.deltaX < 0 && anime.set(this.slideImages, {
                        transformOrigin: "right center"
                    }), 0 < ev.deltaX && anime.set(this.slideImages, {
                        transformOrigin: "left center"
                    })
                }.bind(this)), this.createCache(), this.inView()
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslate: function(event) {
                var oldCurrent = this.current;
                this.current = event.item.index, this.updatePagination(this.current), this.updateText(oldCurrent, this.current), anime({
                    targets: this.slideImages,
                    scaleX: [1.1, 1],
                    easing: "easeOutQuint",
                    duration: 800
                })
            }.bind(this),
            onDrag: function(event) {
                anime({
                    targets: this.slideImages,
                    scaleX: 1.05,
                    easing: "easeOutQuint",
                    duration: 600
                })
            }.bind(this)
        }) : (this.imageSlider.removeClass("owl-carousel"), this.createCache(), this.inView())
    }, Carousel.prototype.inView = function() {
        var that = this,
            currentItem = this.cache[this.current],
            line = this.textContainer.find(".carousel__text__line").get();
        if (this.button.attr("data-url", currentItem.link), $(currentItem.title).css({
                overflow: "hidden",
                display: "inline-block",
                verticalAlign: "bottom",
                opacity: 1
            }).wrapInner($("<span/>", {
                css: {
                    display: "inline-block",
                    verticalAlign: "bottom",
                    opacity: 0
                }
            })), this.playAllAnimation) {
            if (1 < this.slidesLength) var $progressLine = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__line, .s-prog__marker"),
                $sliderNum = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__count").css({
                    overflow: "hidden"
                }).wrapInner("<span/>").children().css({
                    display: "block"
                }).get();
            anime.set(this.button.get(), {
                opacity: 0
            }), anime.set(line, {
                scaleX: 0,
                transformOrigin: "left center"
            }), anime.set($sliderNum, {
                translateY: 200
            }), that.playImageAnimation && anime.set(this.imageSlider.get(), {
                scale: 2,
                opacity: 0
            }), this.playImageAnimation && anime.set(this.imagesContiner.get(), {
                clipPath: that.alt ? "inset(100% 0 0 0)" : "inset(45% 20%)"
            }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
                isInView && (this.destroy(), that.playImageAnimation && anime({
                    targets: that.imagesContiner.get(),
                    clipPath: that.alt ? ["inset(100% 0% 0% 0%)", "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)"] : ["inset(50% 20%)", "inset(0%)"],
                    duration: 1300,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), that.playImageAnimation && anime({
                    targets: that.imageSlider.get(),
                    scale: 1,
                    opacity: [0, 1],
                    duration: 1500,
                    delay: 300,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), anime({
                    targets: that.button.get(),
                    translateY: [200, 0],
                    opacity: [0, 1],
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), anime({
                    targets: $(currentItem.title).children().get(),
                    translateY: [200, 0],
                    opacity: [1, 1],
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), anime({
                    targets: line,
                    scaleX: 1.001,
                    duration: 1500,
                    delay: 602,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), currentItem.subTitle.forEach(function(line, index) {
                    anime({
                        targets: line,
                        translateY: [400 + 300 * index, 0],
                        opacity: [1, 1],
                        delay: 50 * index + 100,
                        easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                    })
                }), anime({
                    targets: currentItem.desc,
                    translateY: [200, 0],
                    opacity: [0, 1],
                    delay: 300,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), 1 < that.slidesLength && (anime({
                    targets: $progressLine.get(),
                    width: function(el) {
                        return [0, el.offsetWidth]
                    },
                    duration: 1300,
                    delay: 1400,
                    easing: "easeOutQuint"
                }), anime({
                    targets: $sliderNum,
                    translateY: 0,
                    duration: 1300,
                    delay: anime.stagger(200, {
                        start: 1200
                    }),
                    easing: "easeOutQuint"
                })))
            })
        } else anime.set(that.button.get().concat($(currentItem.title).children().get()).concat(currentItem.desc), {
            translateY: 0,
            opacity: 1
        }), anime.set(line, {
            scaleX: 1.001
        }), currentItem.subTitle.forEach(function(line, index) {
            anime.set(line, {
                translateY: 0,
                opacity: 1
            })
        }), 1 < that.slidesLength && (anime.set($progressLine.get(), {
            targets: $progressLine.get(),
            width: function(el) {
                return el.offsetWidth
            }
        }), anime.set($sliderNum, {
            translateY: 0
        }))
    }, Carousel.prototype.updateText = function(prev, next) {
        if (!(prev === next || this.cache.length < 2)) {
            var nextItem = this.cache[next],
                currentItem = this.cache[prev],
                itemsToReset = this.cache.filter(function(item, index) {
                    return index !== prev
                });
            this.button.attr("data-url", nextItem.link), itemsToReset.forEach(function(item) {
                anime.set(item.desc, {
                    opacity: 0
                })
            }), anime({
                targets: this.textContainer.get(),
                height: this.textSlideItems.eq(this.current).height(),
                duration: 2e3,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: currentItem.title,
                translateY: [0, -50],
                opacity: [1, 0],
                duration: 1300,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }), currentItem.subTitle.forEach(function(line, index) {
                anime({
                    targets: line,
                    translateY: [0, -400],
                    opacity: [1, 0],
                    duration: 1500,
                    delay: 150 * index + 100,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                })
            }), anime({
                targets: currentItem.desc,
                translateY: [0, 50],
                opacity: [1, 0],
                duration: 1500,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: nextItem.title,
                translateY: [50, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                duration: 1300,
                delay: 300,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }), nextItem.subTitle.forEach(function(line, index) {
                anime({
                    targets: line,
                    translateY: [400 + 300 * index, 0],
                    opacity: [0, 1],
                    duration: 1500,
                    delay: 50 * index + 200,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                })
            }), anime({
                targets: nextItem.desc,
                translateY: [100, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                duration: 1500,
                delay: 500,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            })
        }
    }, Carousel.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        })
    }, Carousel.prototype.resize = function() {
        window.outerWidth < app.MD_BREAKPOINT ? this.images.css("height", window.innerHeight) : this.images.css("height", ""), this.textContainer.height(this.textSlideItems.eq(this.current).height())
    }, Carousel.prototype.destroy = function() {
        1 < this.slidesLength && (this.imageSlider.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), this.hammertime.destroy()), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.inviewInstance && this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.button.off("hold")
    }, Carousel.prototype.createCache = function() {
        this.textSlideItems.each(function(index, item) {
            var meta = {},
                $el = $(item),
                split = Splitting({
                    target: $el.find('h2:not(".title")').get(),
                    by: "lines"
                });
            app.wrapLines(split[0].lines), meta.title = $el.find(".title").get(), meta.subTitle = split[0].lines, meta.desc = $el.find("p").get(), meta.link = $el.data("url"), anime.set([meta.title, meta.subTitle, meta.desc], {
                opacity: 0
            }), this.cache.push(meta)
        }.bind(this))
    }, Carousel.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "resize", "inView", "updatePagination", "createCache", "updateText"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Carousel = Carousel
}(), app.MOBILE = "mobile", app.DESKTOP = "desktop", app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT = "540", app.LG_BREAKPOINT = "991", app.MD_BREAKPOINT = "767", app.animationDuration = 1290, app.animationStagger = 80, app.isMobileDevice = document.body.hasAttribute("data-mobile-device"), app.holdTime = 1800;
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function Cursor(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.cursorInner = this.el.find(".cursor-inner"), this.cursorRipple = this.el.find(".cursor-ripple"), this.hoverCursorSvg = null, this.holdBtnLottie = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.cursorInner[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: app.cursor.holdBtn,
            rendererSettings: {
                className: "lottie-hold-button"
            }
        }), this.rippleLottie = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.cursorRipple[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: app.cursor.lottieRipple,
            rendererSettings: {
                className: "ripple-lottie"
            }
        }), this.holdBtnLottie.addEventListener("DOMLoaded", function() {
            this.hoverCursorSvg = this.cursorInner.find(".lottie-hold-button"), this.hoverCursorSvg.css("opacity", 0)
        }.bind(this)), this.holdBtnLottie.onEnterFrame = function(e) {
            var prevDuration = this.playDuration;
            this.playDuration = e.currentTime;
            var direction = e.currentTime < prevDuration;
            90 < e.currentTime && 1 === direction && this.holdBtnLottie.pause()
        }.bind(this), $("body").addClass("custom-cursor"), $(window).one("mousemove", function() {
            this.init(), this.el.css("display", "block"), $(window).on("mousemove", this.handleMouseMove)
        }.bind(this))
    }
    Cursor.prototype.init = function() {
        var that = this,
            cursor = this.el[0],
            cursorInner = this.cursorInner[0];
        $("body").on("click", "a:not(.hero-link):not([data-hold-btn]):not(.chosen-single)", function() {
            this.rippleLottie.goToAndPlay(0, !0)
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseenter", "button, a, input, .clickable, textarea", function(e) {
            var parent = e.currentTarget;
            $(parent).children("[data-cursor]").length || (cursor.style.width = "30px", cursor.style.height = "30px", cursorInner.style.borderWidth = "2px", cursorInner.style.borderColor = "#fe5c01")
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseleave", "button, input, a, .clickable, textarea", function(e) {
            var parent = e.currentTarget;
            $(parent).children("[data-cursor]").length || (cursor.style.width = "", cursor.style.height = "", cursorInner.style.borderWidth = "", cursorInner.style.borderColor = "#a8a8a8")
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseenter", "[data-cursor]", function(e) {
            var parent = e.currentTarget,
                type = parent.getAttribute("data-cursor"),
                el = $(parent).find("[data-cursor-inner]")[0];
            if (that.resetTimeout && clearTimeout(that.resetTimeout), this.el.addClass("on-link"), "circle" === type) cursor.style.width = Math.min(el.clientWidth + 30, 162) + "px", cursor.style.height = Math.min(el.clientWidth + 30, 162) + "px", cursorInner.style.borderColor = "transparent", that.holdBtnLottie.setDirection(1), that.holdBtnLottie.setSpeed(1), that.holdBtnLottie.play(), that.hoverCursorSvg.css("opacity", 1);
            else {
                var line = $(parent).closest("a").find(".line");
                that.hoverCursorSvg.css("opacity", 0), TweenMax.to(line, .3, {
                    scaleX: 0
                }), cursor.style.width = el.clientWidth + 48 + "px", cursor.style.height = el.clientHeight + 18 + "px", cursorInner.style.borderRadius = "30px", cursorInner.style.borderWidth = "2px", cursorInner.style.borderColor = "#fe5c01"
            }
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseleave", "[data-cursor]", function(e) {
            var parent = e.currentTarget,
                type = parent.getAttribute("data-cursor"),
                el = $(parent).find("[data-cursor-inner]")[0];
            if (TweenMax.to(el, .3, {
                    x: 0,
                    y: 0
                }), this.el.removeClass("on-link"), "circle" === type) cursor.style.width = "", cursor.style.height = "", that.holdBtnLottie.setDirection(-1), that.holdBtnLottie.setSpeed(2), that.holdBtnLottie.play(), that.resetTimeout = setTimeout(function() {
                cursorInner.style.borderColor = "", that.hoverCursorSvg.css("opacity", 1)
            }, 1e3);
            else {
                var line = $(parent).closest("a").find(".line");
                TweenMax.to(line, .3, {
                    scaleX: 1
                }), cursor.style.width = "", cursor.style.height = "", cursorInner.style.borderRadius = "", cursorInner.style.borderWidth = "", cursorInner.style.borderColor = ""
            }
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseenter", ".owl-carousel", function(e) {
            this.el.addClass("on-slider")
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseleave", ".owl-carousel", function(e) {
            this.el.removeClass("on-slider")
        }.bind(this)).on("mousemove", "[data-cursor]:not([data-cursor-no-move])", function(e) {
            var parent = e.currentTarget,
                el = $(parent).find("[data-cursor-inner]")[0],
                hoverEl = $(parent).find("[data-cursor-hover]")[0],
                elBounds = parent.getBoundingClientRect(),
                transX = e.clientX - elBounds.left - .5 * elBounds.width,
                transY = e.clientY - elBounds.top - .5 * elBounds.height;
            transX = transX.clamp(-.5 * hoverEl.clientWidth, .5 * hoverEl.clientWidth), transY = transY.clamp(-.5 * hoverEl.clientHeight, .5 * hoverEl.clientHeight), TweenMax.to(el, 1, {
                x: transX,
                y: transY,
                ease: Power2.easeOut
            })
        }.bind(this))
    }, Cursor.prototype.resetCursor = function(e) {
        var cursor = this.el[0],
            cursorInner = this.cursorInner[0];
        cursor.style.width = "", cursor.style.height = "", cursorInner.style.borderRadius = "", cursorInner.style.borderWidth = "", cursorInner.style.borderColor = "", cursorInner.style.borderColor = "", this.hoverCursorSvg.css("opacity", 1), this.el.removeClass("on-slider"), this.holdBtnLottie.setDirection(-1), this.holdBtnLottie.setSpeed(2), this.holdBtnLottie.play()
    }, Cursor.prototype.handleMouseMove = function(e) {
        TweenMax.to(this.el, .2, {
            left: e.clientX,
            top: e.clientY
        })
    }, Cursor.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "handleMouseMove", "resetCursor"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Cursor = Cursor
}();
var app = app || {};

    function DataRectBtn(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.timeout = null, this.svgBtn = this.el.find("svg"), this.text = this.el.find(".text"), this.textAlt = this.text.clone().css({
            top: "24px",
            opacity: 0,
            color: "#ffffff"
        }), this.hammer = new Hammer.Manager(this.el[0]), this.svgBtn.hide(), this.viewed = !1, this.init()
    }
    DataRectBtn.prototype.init = function() {
        var that = this;
        this.text.css("top", "4px").after(this.textAlt), this.lottieBtn = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.el[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: app.lottie.rectBtn,
            rendererSettings: {
                className: ""
            }
        }), this.el.on("mouseenter", function() {
            that.viewed || (this.viewed = !0, that.lottieBtn.goToAndPlay(208, !0)), textTween = TweenMax.to(that.text, .3, {
                opacity: 0,
                top: "-16px",
                delay: 1.1
            }), textTween2 = TweenMax.to(that.textAlt, .3, {
                opacity: 1,
                top: "4px",
                delay: 1.1
            }), that.lottieBtn.setDirection(1), that.lottieBtn.play()
        }).on("mouseleave", function() {
            textTween && textTween.kill(), textTween2 && textTween2.kill(), TweenMax.to(that.text, .3, {
                opacity: 1,
                top: "4px",
                delay: .3
            }), TweenMax.to(that.textAlt, .3, {
                opacity: 0,
                top: "24px",
                delay: .3
            }), that.lottieBtn.setDirection(-1), that.lottieBtn.play()
        }), this.lottieBtn.onEnterFrame = function(e) {
            if (200 < e.currentTime && !this.viewed) {
                this.viewed = !0, this.lottieBtn.pause()
            } else e.currentTime < 200 && this.viewed && this.lottieBtn.pause()
        }.bind(this), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), that.lottieBtn.play())
        })
    }, DataRectBtn.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.hammer.destroy(), this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.el.off("mouseenter", "mouseleave")
    }, DataRectBtn.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.DataRectBtn = DataRectBtn
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function ExprtzListSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.mode = app.MOBILE, this.init()
    }
    ExprtzListSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized"), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.resize(), this.inView()
    }, ExprtzListSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var slideAnimInstances = [],
            owlSlides = this.el.find(".owl-item"),
            winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            slidesInView = owlSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
                var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
            });
        slidesInView.each(function(index, slide) {
            slideAnimInstances.push(new app.AnimateExptzBlc($(slide))), anime.set(slidesInView.get(), {
                translateX: function(item, index) {
                    return (index + 1) * (1.2 * winWidth)
                },
                clipPath: "inset(0 0 0 100%)",
                scale: function(item, index) {
                    return 2 * (index + 1)
                }
            })
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateX: 0,
                scale: 1,
                clipPath: {
                    value: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
                    duration: 3e3
                },
                duration: 2200,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(200)
            }), slideAnimInstances.forEach(function(item, index) {
                setTimeout(function() {
                    item.reveal()
                }, 100 * index)
            }))
        })
    }, ExprtzListSlider.prototype.resize = function() {
        window.innerWidth > app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.MOBILE ? (this.mode = app.DESKTOP, this.el.owlCarousel({
            loop: !1,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            margin: 45,
            autoWidth: !0
        })) : window.innerWidth <= app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.DESKTOP && (this.mode = app.MOBILE, this.el.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"))
    }, ExprtzListSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.el.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.inviewInstance.destroy()
    }, ExprtzListSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView", "resize"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.ExprtzListSlider = ExprtzListSlider
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function ExprtzSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.initSlides = null, this.init()
    }
    ExprtzSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized");
        var $margin = 45;
        $(window).width() < 767 && ($margin = 20), this.el.owlCarousel({
            loop: !1,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            margin: $margin,
            autoWidth: !0
        }), this.inView()
    }, ExprtzSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var slideAnimInstances = [],
            owlSlides = this.el.find(".owl-item"),
            winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            slidesInView = owlSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
                var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
            });
        slidesInView.each(function(index, slide) {
            slideAnimInstances.push(new app.AnimateExptzBlc($(slide))), anime.set(slidesInView.get(), {
                translateX: function(item, index) {
                    return (index + 1) * (1.2 * winWidth)
                },
                clipPath: "inset(0 0 0 100%)",
                scale: function(item, index) {
                    return 2 * (index + 1)
                }
            })
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateX: 0,
                scale: 1,
                clipPath: {
                    value: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
                    duration: 3e3
                },
                duration: 2200,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(200)
            }), slideAnimInstances.forEach(function(item, index) {
                setTimeout(function() {
                    item.reveal()
                }, 100 * index)
            }))
        })
    }, ExprtzSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.el.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), this.inviewInstance.destroy()
    }, ExprtzSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.ExprtzSlider = ExprtzSlider

! function() {
    function Form(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.select = this.el.find("select"), this.input = this.el.find("input:not([type=file]), input:not([type=range]), textarea"), this.file = this.el.find("input[type=file]"), this.range = this.el.find("input[type=range]"), this.wcfRadioBtn = this.el.find(".wpcf7-radio input[type=radio]"), this.fileButton = this.el.find(".upload-button"), this.init()
    }
    Form.prototype.init = function() {
        this.select.each(function(index, item) {
            $select = $(item), $select.hasClass("wpcf7-select") && !app.isMobileDevice && $select.prepend($('<option value="" selected="selected">&nbsp;</option>'))
        }), this.select.chosen({
            disable_search_threshold: 100,
            placeholder_text_single: " "
        }), this.select.on("change", function() {
            $(this).val() ? $(this).closest(".form-field").removeClass("empty") : $(this).closest(".form-field").addClass("empty")
        }), this.input.on("keyup", function() {
            $(this).val() ? $(this).closest(".form-field").removeClass("empty") : $(this).closest(".form-field").addClass("empty")
        }), this.file.on("change", function(e) {
            var text = $(this).closest(".form-field").find(".upload-text");
            e.target.files.length ? (text.text(e.target.files[0].name), $(this).closest(".form-field").removeClass("empty")) : (text.html("&nbsp;"), $(this).closest(".form-field").addClass("empty"))
        }), this.fileButton.on("click", function(e) {
            e.preventDefault(), $(this).closest(".form-field").find("input[type=file]").trigger("click")
        }), this.range.rangeslider({
            polyfill: !1,
            onSlide: function(position, value) {
                $(this.$element).closest(".form-field").find(".range-current").text("AED " + app.formatNumber(value))
            }
        }), this.wcfRadioBtn.each(function(index, item) {
            var el = $(item),
                id = el.attr("name") + Math.random(),
                radioParent = el.closest(".radio-buttons"),
                radioText = el.prev(".wpcf7-list-item-label").text();
            el.closest(".wpcf7-list-item").remove(), el.attr("id", id), radioParent.append(el), el.after($("<label/>", {
                for: id,
                text: radioText
            }))
        }), this.file.trigger("change"), this.select.trigger("change"), this.input.trigger("keyup")
    }, Form.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.select.chosen("destroy"), this.file.off("change"), this.select.off("change"), this.input.off("keyup"), this.range.rangeslider("destroy"), this.fileButton.off("click")
    }, Form.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Form = Form
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function GCB(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.mode = 991 < window.innerWidth ? app.DESKTOP : app.MOBILE, this.slidesToShow = this.mode === app.DESKTOP ? 10 : 6, this.grid = this.el.find(".gbl-clts-blc__grid.unintialized"), this.items = this.grid.children(), this.cloneditems = this.items.clone(), this.parked = this.items.filter(":gt(" + (this.slidesToShow - 1) + ")").clone().get(), this.items.filter(":gt(" + (this.slidesToShow - 1) + ")").remove(), this.grid.removeClass("unintialized"), this.items = this.grid.children(), this.timeAmount = 3e3, this.lastSwapped = 0, this.playing = !1, this.destroyed = !1, this.initialInview = !1, this.inView(), $(window).on("resize", this.resize)
    }
    GCB.prototype.init = function() {}, GCB.prototype.inView = function() {
        var that = this;
        anime.set(this.items.get(), {
            opacity: 0,
            translateY: 20
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            if (isInView) {
                if (that.initialInview || (that.initialInview = !0, anime({
                        targets: that.items.get(),
                        opacity: [0, 1],
                        translateY: [20, 0],
                        easing: "easeOutQuint",
                        duration: 2400,
                        delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger)
                    })), that.playing) return;
                if (that.playing = !0, !that.parked.length) return;
                that.gridTimeout = setTimeout(that.swap, 400)
            } else {
                if (!that.playing) return;
                that.playing = !1, that.gridTimeout && (clearTimeout(that.gridTimeout), that.gridTimeout = null)
            }
        })
    }, GCB.prototype.resize = function() {
        var newMode = 991 < window.innerWidth ? app.DESKTOP : app.MOBILE;
        this.mode != newMode && (this.mode = newMode, clearTimeout(this.gridTimeout), this.slidesToShow = this.mode === app.DESKTOP ? 10 : 6, this.grid.html(this.cloneditems.clone()), this.items = this.grid.children(), this.parked = this.items.filter(":gt(" + (this.slidesToShow - 1) + ")").clone().get(), this.items.filter(":gt(" + (this.slidesToShow - 1) + ")").remove(), this.items = this.grid.children(), this.gridTimeout = setTimeout(this.swap, this.timeAmount))
    }, GCB.prototype.swap = function() {
        if (this.parked.length) {
            for (var itemToSwap = app.randomNumber(0, this.parked.length - 1), itemToSwapWith = app.randomNumber(0, this.slidesToShow - 1); itemToSwap === this.lastSwapped;) itemToSwap = app.randomNumber(0, this.parked.length - 1);
            this.lastSwapped = itemToSwap, anime({
                targets: this.items.eq(itemToSwapWith).find("img").get(),
                opacity: [1, 0],
                scale: [1, .8],
                duration: 600,
                easing: "easeInSine",
                complete: function() {
                    var clone = this.items.eq(itemToSwapWith).clone()[0],
                        toShow = this.parked.splice(itemToSwap, 1, clone)[0];
                    this.items.eq(itemToSwapWith).replaceWith(toShow), this.items = this.grid.children(), anime({
                        targets: this.items.eq(itemToSwapWith).find("img").get(),
                        opacity: [0, 1],
                        scale: [1.2, 1],
                        duration: 1e3,
                        easing: "easeInSine",
                        complete: function() {
                            this.destroyed || (this.gridTimeout = setTimeout(this.swap, this.timeAmount))
                        }.bind(this)
                    })
                }.bind(this)
            })
        }
    }, GCB.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.inviewInstance && this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.destroyed = !0, this.gridTimeout && (clearTimeout(this.gridTimeout), this.gridTimeout = null)
    }, GCB.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView", "swap", "resize"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.GlobalClientsBlock = GCB
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function GenBlcSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slider = this.el.find(".genslider-blc__slides"), this.slidesToshow = this.slider.data("slides"), this.slides = this.slider.find(".genslider-blc__slide"), this.pagination = this.el.find(".genslider-blc__foot"), this.initSlides = null, this.soundCloudInstances = [], this.init()
    }
    GenBlcSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized"), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.slides.each(function(index, item) {
            item.setAttribute("data-index", index)
        });
        var responsive = {
            loop: !0,
            margin: 20,
            center: !0
        };
        if (1 == this.slidesToshow) responsive = {
            loop: !0,
            margin: 20,
            center: !1,
            autoWidth: !1,
            items: 1
        };
        if (2 == this.slidesToshow) responsive = {
            loop: !0,
            margin: 20,
            center: !1,
            autoWidth: !1,
            items: 2
        };
        if (3 == this.slidesToshow) responsive = {
            loop: !0,
            margin: 20,
            center: !1,
            autoWidth: !1,
            items: 3
        };
        this.slider.owlCarousel({
            loop: !1,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            items: 1,
            autoWidth: !0,
            margin: 10,
            responsive: {
                540: {
                    loop: !0,
                    margin: 20,
                    center: !0
                },
                991: responsive
            },
            onInitialized: function() {
                this.resize(), this.initSlides = this.slider.find(".owl-item"), this.initSlides.find(".soundcloud-blc").each(function(index, el) {
                    this.soundCloudInstances.push(new app.SoundCloud($(el)))
                }.bind(this))
            }.bind(this),
            onRefreshed: function(event) {
                this.initSlides = this.slider.find(".owl-item")
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: function(event) {
                this.updatePagination(540 <= window.innerWidth ? this.initSlides.filter(".active").first().children().data("index") : event.item.index)
            }.bind(this)
        }), this.pagination.append(app.getSliderPagination((this.slides.length < 9 ? "0" : "") + this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.inView()
    }, GenBlcSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var $progressLine = this.el.find(".s-prog__line, .s-prog__marker"),
            $sliderNum = this.el.find(".s-prog__count").css({
                overflow: "hidden"
            }).wrapInner("<span/>").children().css({
                display: "block"
            }).get(),
            owlSlides = this.slider.find(".owl-item"),
            winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            slidesInView = owlSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
                var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
            });
        anime.set(slidesInView.get(), {
            translateX: function(item, index) {
                return (index + 1) * (1.5 * winWidth)
            },
            clipPath: "inset(0 0 0 100%)",
            scale: function(item, index) {
                return 2 * (index + 1)
            }
        }), anime.set($sliderNum, {
            translateY: "100%"
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.slider[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateX: 0,
                scale: 1,
                clipPath: {
                    value: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
                    duration: 2700
                },
                duration: 2500,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: 600
            }), anime({
                targets: $progressLine.get(),
                width: function(el) {
                    return [0, el.offsetWidth]
                },
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: $sliderNum,
                translateY: "0%",
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1600,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }))
        })
    }, GenBlcSlider.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        })
    }, GenBlcSlider.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.paginationMarker && (this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.updatePagination(this.current))
    }, GenBlcSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.slider.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.soundCloudInstances.forEach(function(item) {
            item.destroy()
        })
    }, GenBlcSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.GenBlcSlider = GenBlcSlider
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function GBS(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slider = this.el.find(".glb-blc__slider"), this.slides = this.slider.children(), this.initSlides = this.slides, this.contactUsBtn = this.el.find(".glb-blc__btn.hold__btn"), this.nearestBtn = this.el.find(".dynamic-nearest-location"), this.cancelToken = axios.CancelToken, this.source = null, this.init()
    }
    GBS.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.slider.removeClass("uninitialized"), this.slider.owlCarousel({
            loop: !0,
            center: !0,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            smartSpeed: 500,
            autoWidth: !0,
            onInitialized: function() {
                this.initSlides = this.slider.find(".glb-blc__slide"), this.initSlides.each(function(index, el) {
                    $(el).find(".time-zones .item").first().addClass("active")
                }), this.resize(), this.translated(), this.inView()
            }.bind(this),
            onRefreshed: function() {
                this.initSlides = this.slider.find(".glb-blc__slide"), this.resize()
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: this.translated,
            onDrag: this.translate
        }), this.nearestLocation(), this.resize()
    }, GBS.prototype.nearestLocation = function() {
        var that = this,
            nLoc = sessionStorage.getItem("nLoc");
        nLoc ? (nLoc = JSON.parse(nLoc)) && (that.nearestBtn.attr("href", nLoc.link), that.nearestBtn.attr("title", nLoc.title), that.nearestBtn.find(".city-name").text(nLoc.title)) : (this.source && this.source.cancel(), this.source = this.cancelToken.source(), $.get("https://ipinfo.io", function(response) {
            var loc = response.loc.split(",");
            axios({
                cancelToken: that.source.token,
                method: "post",
                url: apiroutes.nearestLocation,
                data: {
                    lat: loc[0],
                    long: loc[1]
                }
            }).then(function(response) {
                var data = response.data;
                that.nearestBtn.attr("href", data.link), that.nearestBtn.attr("title", data.title), that.nearestBtn.find(".city-name").text(data.title), sessionStorage.setItem("nLoc", JSON.stringify(data))
            })
        }, "jsonp"))
    }, GBS.prototype.inView = function() {
        var owlSlides = this.initSlides.parent(),
            winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            bgColor = this.el.css("background-color"),
            bgColorEl = $("<div/>", {
                css: {
                    position: "absolute",
                    left: 0,
                    top: 0,
                    width: "100%",
                    height: "100%",
                    backgroundColor: bgColor
                }
            }).prependTo(this.el),
            activeEl = this.slider.find(".owl-item.active.center"),
            prev = (activeEl.find(".time-zones .item"), activeEl.prev()),
            prev2 = prev.prev(),
            prevAll = prev2.prevAll(),
            next = activeEl.next(),
            next2 = next.next(),
            nextAll = next2.nextAll();
        TweenMax.set(prev, {
            opacity: .3,
            scale: .8
        }), TweenMax.set(next, {
            opacity: .3,
            scale: .8
        }), TweenMax.set(prev2, {
            opacity: .1,
            scale: .6,
            x: "40px"
        }), TweenMax.set(next2, {
            opacity: .1,
            scale: .6,
            x: "-40px"
        }), TweenMax.set(prevAll, {
            opacity: 0,
            scale: .4
        }), TweenMax.set(nextAll, {
            opacity: 0,
            scale: .4
        });
        var slidesInView = owlSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
            var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
            return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
        });
        this.el.css({
            backgroundColor: "transparent",
            position: "relative"
        }), anime.set(bgColorEl.get(), {
            scaleY: "0",
            transformOrigin: "center bottom"
        }), setTimeout(function() {
            anime.set(slidesInView.get(), {
                translateX: function(item, index) {
                    return (index + 1) * (1.5 * winWidth)
                },
                clipPath: "inset(0 0 0 100%)",
                scale: function(item, index) {
                    return 2 * (index + 1)
                }
            })
        }, 400), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.slider[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: bgColorEl.get(),
                scaleY: 1,
                duration: 1700,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateX: 0,
                scale: 1,
                clipPath: {
                    value: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
                    duration: 2700
                },
                duration: 2500,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: 600
            }))
        })
    }, GBS.prototype.translate = function(e) {
        var slides = this.slider.find(".owl-item");
        TweenMax.to(slides, .2, {
            opacity: .1,
            x: 0,
            y: 0,
            scale: 1
        })
    }, GBS.prototype.translated = function() {
        this.slideTimer && (clearInterval(this.slideTimer), this.slideTimer = null);
        var activeEl = this.slider.find(".owl-item.active.center"),
            timeZones = activeEl.find(".time-zones .item"),
            prev = activeEl.prev(),
            prev2 = prev.prev(),
            prevAll = prev2.prevAll(),
            next = activeEl.next(),
            next2 = next.next(),
            nextAll = next2.nextAll();
        this.contactUsBtn.attr("href", activeEl.find(".glb-blc__slide.item").data("link")), TweenMax.to(activeEl, .2, {
            opacity: 1
        }), TweenMax.to(prev, .2, {
            opacity: .3,
            scale: .8
        }), TweenMax.to(next, .2, {
            opacity: .3,
            scale: .8
        }), TweenMax.to(prev2, .2, {
            opacity: .1,
            scale: .6,
            x: "40px"
        }), TweenMax.to(next2, .2, {
            opacity: .1,
            scale: .6,
            x: "-40px"
        }), TweenMax.to(prevAll, .2, {
            opacity: 0,
            scale: .4
        }), TweenMax.to(nextAll, .2, {
            opacity: 0,
            scale: .4
        }), 1 < timeZones.length && (this.slideTimer = setInterval(function() {
            var current = timeZones.filter(".active");
            current.index() !== timeZones.length - 1 ? current.removeClass("active").next().addClass("active") : (current.removeClass("active"), timeZones.first().addClass("active")), anime({
                targets: activeEl.find(".time-zones .wrapper").get(),
                translateY: current.height() * timeZones.filter(".active").index() * -1,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            })
        }, 4e3))
    }, GBS.prototype.resize = function() {
        var tz = this.initSlides.find(".time-zones");
        tz.height(tz.first().find(".item").height()), tz.each(function(index, el) {
            anime({
                targets: $(el).find(".wrapper").get(),
                translateY: $(el).find(".item").height() * Math.max($(el).find(".item.active").index(), 0) * -1
            })
        })
    }, GBS.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.inviewInstance && this.inviewInstance.destroy(), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.slideTimer && (clearInterval(this.slideTimer), this.slideTimer = null), this.slider.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel")
    }, GBS.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView", "resize", "translated", "translate", "nearestLocation"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.GlobalBlockSlider = GBS
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function Glide(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.dom = {}, this.dom.list = this.el.find("ul"), this.dom.items = this.dom.list.children(), this.dom.images = this.el.find(".glide__images"), this.dom.imagesInner = this.dom.images.children(), this.dom.imagesItems = this.dom.imagesInner.children(), this.isWindows = -1 < navigator.platform.indexOf("Win"), this.listHeight = this.dom.list.outerHeight(!0, !0), this.itemHeight = this.dom.items.outerHeight(!0, !0), this.vars = {
            target: 0,
            current: 0,
            bounding: this.listHeight - (window.outerHeight - 500),
            active: 0,
            running: !1
        }, this.inView()
    }
    Glide.prototype.init = function() {
        this.setEvents(), window.requestAnimationFrame(this.animate)
    }, Glide.prototype.inView = function() {
        var that = this,
            winHeight = window.outerHeight;
        anime.set(this.dom.imagesItems.first().nextAll().get(), {
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(this.dom.items.get(), {
            translateY: winHeight
        }), anime.set(this.dom.images.get(), {
            clipPath: "inset(100% 0 0 0)"
        }), anime.set(this.dom.imagesInner.get(), {
            scale: 2
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            if (isInView) {
                this.destroy();
                var obj = {
                    x: 100
                };
                anime({
                    targets: obj,
                    x: 0,
                    duration: 2e3,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint",
                    update: function() {
                        anime.set(that.dom.images.get(), {
                            clipPath: "inset(" + obj.x + "% 0 0 0)"
                        })
                    }
                }), anime({
                    targets: that.dom.imagesInner.get(),
                    scale: 1,
                    duration: 2500,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), anime({
                    targets: that.dom.items.get(),
                    translateY: 0,
                    duration: 4e3,
                    easing: "spring(1, 80, 10, 0)",
                    delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                        start: 1e3
                    }),
                    complete: function() {
                        that.init()
                    }
                })
            }
        })
    }, Glide.prototype.setEvents = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.handleResize), this.el.on("mousewheel", this.handleMouseWheel), this.dom.items.addClass("no-barba").on("mouseenter", this.handleMouseover).on("click", this.handleLinkClick), $(document).on("touchmove", this.handleSwipe), $(document).on("touchend", this.handleTouchEnd)
    }, Glide.prototype.handleResize = function() {
        this.resizing = !0, this.listHeight = this.dom.list.outerHeight(!0, !0), this.itemHeight = this.dom.items.outerHeight(!0, !0), this.vars.bounding = this.listHeight - (window.outerHeight - 500), this.resizing = !1
    }, Glide.prototype.handleTouchEnd = function(e) {
        this.prevTouch = void 0
    }, Glide.prototype.handleSwipe = function(e) {
        this.vars.target -= e.touches[0].clientY - (this.prevTouch || e.touches[0].clientY), this.clampTarget(), this.prevTouch = e.touches[0].clientY
    }, Glide.prototype.handleMouseover = function(e) {
        this.activateActive($(e.currentTarget))
    }, Glide.prototype.activateActive = function($active) {
        var $prev = $active.prev(),
            $next = $active.next(),
            $closest = $prev.get().concat($next.get()),
            $siblings = $prev.prevAll().get().concat($next.nextAll().get());
        if ($active.hasClass("active")) return !1;
        $active.addClass("active").siblings().removeClass("active"), TweenMax.set(this.dom.imagesItems, {
            opacity: 0,
            ease: Expo.easeOut
        }), TweenMax.to(this.dom.imagesItems.eq($active.index()), .4, {
            opacity: 1,
            ease: Expo.easeOut
        }), TweenMax.to($active, .6, {
            scale: 640 < window.outerWidth ? 1.2 : 1.08,
            opacity: 1,
            ease: Expo.easeOut
        }), TweenMax.to($closest, .6, {
            scale: 640 < window.outerWidth ? 1.08 : 1.04,
            opacity: .8,
            ease: Expo.easeOut
        }), TweenMax.to($siblings, .6, {
            scale: 1,
            opacity: .6,
            ease: Expo.easeOut
        })
    }, Glide.prototype.handleMouseWheel = function(event) {
        this.vars.target += event.deltaY * (this.isWindows ? -20 : -1.4), this.clampTarget()
    }, Glide.prototype.handleLinkClick = function(e) {
        var that = this,
            $clicked = $(e.currentTarget);
        e.preventDefault(), this.handleMouseover(e), this.destroy(), Barba.Pjax.Cache.set($clicked.find("a").attr("href"), Barba.Utils.xhr($clicked.find("a").attr("href")));
        var winHeight = window.outerHeight,
            itemsToMove = this.dom.items.filter(function(index, item) {
                var bounds = item.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 < bounds.top && bounds.bottom < winHeight || bounds.top < 0 && 0 < bounds.bottom || bounds.top < winHeight && bounds.bottom > winHeight
            });
        anime({
            targets: itemsToMove.get(),
            translateY: -1.5 * window.outerHeight,
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger),
            complete: function() {
                window.BarbaData = {
                    el: that.el,
                    from: "work-list"
                }, Barba.Pjax.goTo($clicked.find("a").attr("href"))
            }
        })
    }, Glide.prototype.clampTarget = function() {
        this.vars.target = Math.round(Math.max(0, Math.min(this.vars.target, this.vars.bounding))), this.vars.running || window.requestAnimationFrame(this.animate)
    }, Glide.prototype.animate = function() {
        if (!this.resizing) {
            this.vars.current += .1 * (this.vars.target - this.vars.current), this.vars.current < .1 && (this.vars.current = 0);
            var activeIndex = Math.min(Math.max(Math.floor(this.vars.current / (this.vars.bounding / this.dom.items.length)), 0), this.dom.items.length - 1);
            this.dom.list.css(getPrefix("transform"), "translateY(-" + this.vars.current + "px)"), activeIndex !== this.vars.active && this.activateActive(this.dom.items.eq(activeIndex)), this.vars.active = activeIndex;
            var diff = this.vars.target - this.vars.current;
            diff < .05 && -.05 < diff ? this.vars.running = !1 : (this.vars.running = !0, window.requestAnimationFrame(this.animate))
        }
    }, Glide.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.inviewInstance.destroy(), $(document).off("touchmove", this.handleSwipe), $(document).off("touchend", this.handleTouchEnd), this.dom.items.off("mouseenter", this.handleMouseover), $(window).off("resize", this.handleResize), this.el.off("mousewheel", this.handleMouseWheel)
    }, Glide.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "handleResize", "animate", "inView", "setEvents", "handleMouseWheel", "handleTouchEnd", "handleSwipe", "clampTarget", "handleMouseover", "handleLinkClick"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Glide = Glide
}();
var app = app || {};

function is_touch_device() {
    var prefixes = " -webkit- -moz- -o- -ms- ".split(" ");
    return !!("ontouchstart" in window || window.DocumentTouch && document instanceof DocumentTouch) || function(query) {
        return window.matchMedia(query).matches
    }(["(", prefixes.join("touch-enabled),("), "heartz", ")"].join(""))
}

function CookiesHelper() {}
app.debounce = function(func, wait, immediate) {
        var timeout;
        return function() {
            var context = this,
                args = arguments,
                callNow = immediate && !timeout;
            clearTimeout(timeout), timeout = setTimeout(function() {
                timeout = null, immediate || func.apply(context, args)
            }, wait), callNow && func.apply(context, args)
        }
    }, Number.prototype.clamp = function(min, max) {
        return Math.min(Math.max(this, min), max)
    }, app.clamp = function(num, min, max) {
        return num <= min ? min : max <= num ? max : num
    }, app.formatNumber = function(val) {
        return 9 < val ? val : val.toFixed(1).replace(/\d(?=(\d{3})+\.)/g, "$&,").replace(".0", "")
    }, app.throttle = function(func, limit) {
        var inThrottle;
        return function() {
            var args = arguments;
            inThrottle || (func.apply(this, args), inThrottle = !0, setTimeout(function() {
                inThrottle = !1
            }, limit))
        }
    }, app.detectIE = function() {
        var ua = window.navigator.userAgent,
            msie = ua.indexOf("MSIE ");
        if (0 < msie) return parseInt(ua.substring(msie + 5, ua.indexOf(".", msie)), 10);
        if (0 < ua.indexOf("Trident/")) {
            var rv = ua.indexOf("rv:");
            return parseInt(ua.substring(rv + 3, ua.indexOf(".", rv)), 10)
        }
        var edge = ua.indexOf("Edge/");
        return 0 < edge && parseInt(ua.substring(edge + 5, ua.indexOf(".", edge)), 10)
    }, app.scrollTop = function(el) {
        function onScroll() {
            100 < $("html").scrollTop() ? el.addClass("show") : el.removeClass("show")
        }
        return el.on("click", function() {
            $("html, body").animate({
                scrollTop: 0
            })
        }), $(window).on("scroll", onScroll), {
            destroy: function() {
                el.removeClass("show"), el.off("click"), $(window).off("scroll", onScroll)
            }
        }
    },
    function(e, t) {
        "object" == typeof exports && "object" == typeof module ? module.exports = t() : "function" == typeof define && define.amd ? define([], t) : "object" == typeof exports ? exports.getPrefix = t() : e.getPrefix = t()
    }(this, function() {
        return e = [function(e, t) {
            "use strict";
            Object.defineProperty(t, "__esModule", {
                value: !0
            }), t.default = function(e) {
                if ("undefined" == typeof document) return e;
                var t = document.createElement("p").style,
                    r = ["ms", "O", "Moz", "Webkit"];
                if ("" === t[e]) return e;
                e = e.charAt(0).toUpperCase() + e.slice(1);
                for (var o = r.length; o--;)
                    if ("" === t[r[o] + e]) return r[o] + e
            }, e.exports = t.default
        }], r = {}, t.m = e, t.c = r, t.p = "dist/", t(0);

        function t(o) {
            if (r[o]) return r[o].exports;
            var n = r[o] = {
                exports: {},
                id: o,
                loaded: !1
            };
            return e[o].call(n.exports, n, n.exports, t), n.loaded = !0, n.exports
        }
        var e, r
    }), app.equalHeight = function(items) {
        items.each(function(index, el) {
            var limit = $(el).data("height-limit") || 768,
                children = $(el).children().css("height", "");
            if (window.innerWidth < limit) return 0;
            var height = 0;
            children.each(function(index, child) {
                height = Math.max(child.offsetHeight, height)
            }), children.css("height", height)
        })
    }, app.wrapLines = function(lines, wrapWords) {
        lines.forEach(function(line) {
            wrapWords && line.forEach(function(word) {
                app.wrapWords(word, !1)
            }), anime.set(line, {
                opacity: 0,
                translateY: "100%",
                verticalAlign: "bottom",
                display: "inline-block"
            })
        })
    }, app.wrapWords = function(word, move) {
        var translate = translate || !0;
        $(word).css({
            display: "inline-block",
            verticalAlign: "bottom"
        }).wrap($("<span/>", {
            css: {
                overflow: "hidden",
                display: "inline-block",
                verticalAlign: "bottom"
            }
        })), translate && anime.set(word, {
            translateY: "100%"
        })
    }, app.getSliderPagination = function(total) {
        for (var el = $('<div class="s-prog"><span class="s-prog__line"></span><span class="s-prog__marker"></span><p class="s-prog__count s-prog__current"></p><p class="s-prog__count s-prog__total">' + total + "</p></div>").clone(), sProg = el.find(".s-prog__count.s-prog__current"), i = 1; i <= parseInt(total); i++) sProg.append($('<span class="item">' + (i < 10 ? "0" : "") + i + "</span>"));
        return el
    }, app.randomNumber = function(min, max) {
        return min = Math.ceil(min), max = Math.floor(max), Math.floor(Math.random() * (max - min + 1)) + min
    }, CookiesHelper.set = function(name, value, days) {
        if (days) {
            var date = new Date;
            date.setTime(date.getTime() + 24 * days * 60 * 60 * 1e3);
            var expires = "; expires=" + date.toGMTString()
        } else expires = "";
        document.cookie = name + "=" + value + expires + "; path=/"
    }, CookiesHelper.get = function(name) {
        for (var nameEQ = name + "=", ca = document.cookie.split(";"), i = 0; i < ca.length; i++) {
            for (var c = ca[i];
                " " == c.charAt(0);) c = c.substring(1, c.length);
            if (0 == c.indexOf(nameEQ)) return c.substring(nameEQ.length, c.length)
        }
        return null
    }, CookiesHelper.eraseCookie = function(name) {
        CookiesHelper.set(name, "", -1)
    };
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function HoldButton(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.hammer = new Hammer.Manager(this.el[0]), this.delay = parseInt(this.el.data("hold-btn")) || 0, this.timeout = null, this.el.addClass("no-barba"), this.init()
    }
    HoldButton.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.on("mouseenter", function() {
            var location = this.el.attr("href") || this.el.data("url") || this.el.data("scroll");
            window.isBarba && Barba.Pjax.Cache.set(location, Barba.Utils.xhr(location)), this.timeout = setTimeout(function() {
                this.openLink(this.el, location)
            }.bind(this), app.holdTime)
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseleave", function() {
            this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout)
        }.bind(this)).on("click", function(e) {
            e.preventDefault(), this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout);
            var location = this.el.attr("href") || this.el.data("url") || this.el.data("scroll");
            this.openLink(this.el, location)
        }.bind(this)), this.hammer.add(new Hammer.Press({
            event: "press",
            pointer: 1,
            threshold: 5,
            time: app.holdTime
        })), this.hammer.on("press", function(event) {
            this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout);
            var location = this.el.attr("href") || this.el.data("url") || this.el.data("scroll");
            this.openLink(this.el, location)
        }.bind(this))
    }, HoldButton.prototype.openLink = function(el, location) {
        this.timeout = null;
        var shouldBlur = this.el[0].hasAttribute("data-blur");
        el.trigger("hold"), setTimeout(function() {
            "_blank" == el.attr("target") ? window.open(location, "_blank") : window.isBarba && (el.attr("href") || el.hasClass("carousel__button")) ? (Barba.Pjax.goTo(location), shouldBlur && $("body").addClass("blur")) : window.location = location
        }.bind(this), this.delay)
    }, HoldButton.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout), this.el.off("click mouseenter mouseleave openLink"), this.hammer.destroy()
    }, HoldButton.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.HoldButton = HoldButton
}();

! function() {
    function ImageSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slider = this.el.find(".img-slider-blc__slides"), this.slides = this.slider.find(".img-slider-blc__slide"), this.pagination = this.el.find(".img-slider-blc__foot"), this.init()
    }
    ImageSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized"), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.slider.owlCarousel({
            loop: !1,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            items: 1,
            onInitialized: function() {
                this.resize()
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: function(event) {
                this.updatePagination(event.item.index)
            }.bind(this)
        }), this.pagination.css("opacity", 0).append(app.getSliderPagination((this.slides.length < 9 ? "0" : "") + this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.inView()
    }, ImageSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var that = this,
            $sliderNum = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__count").wrapInner("<span/>").children().get();
        app.wrapWords($sliderNum), anime.set(this.el.get(), {
            clipPath: "inset(1000% 0 0 0)"
        }), anime.set(this.slider.get(), {
            scale: 2
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: that.pagination.get(),
                opacity: 1,
                duration: 300,
                delay: 1100,
                complete: function() {
                    that.pagination.css("opacity", "")
                }
            }), anime({
                targets: that.el.find(".s-prog__line").get(),
                width: function(el) {
                    return [0, el.offsetWidth]
                },
                duration: 1500,
                delay: 900,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: $sliderNum,
                translateY: 0,
                duration: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(150, {
                    start: 1e3
                })
            }), anime({
                targets: that.el.get(),
                clipPath: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
                duration: 2500,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: that.slider.get(),
                scale: 1,
                duration: 2500,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }))
        })
    }, ImageSlider.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        })
    }, ImageSlider.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.paginationMarker && (this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.updatePagination(this.current))
    }, ImageSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.slider.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.inviewInstance.destroy()
    }, ImageSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.ImageSlider = ImageSlider
}();

! function() {
    function LocationFilter(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.wrapper = this.el.parent(), this.wrapperTop = this.wrapper.offset().top - window.innerHeight, this.init()
    }
    LocationFilter.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("scroll", this.onScroll), $(window).on("resize", this.onResize)
    }, LocationFilter.prototype.onScroll = function() {
