! function() {
    function menu(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.animating = !1, this.isOpen = !1, this.menu = this.el.find(".header-menu"), this.toggleBtn = this.el.find(".menu-toggle"), this.toSlide = $("#content, #footer"), this.overlay = this.el.find(".header-overlay"), this.homeLink = this.el.find(".header__logo--home .header__logo__link"), this.lottieContainer = $("<span/>", {
            class: "home-lottie-container"
        }).appendTo(this.homeLink), this.logoLottie = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.lottieContainer[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: app.lottie.logo,
            rendererSettings: {
                className: "lottie-animation"
            }
        }), this.createCache(), this.init()
    }
    menu.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.css("opacity", 0), $(window).on("scroll", this.handleScroll), this.toggleBtn.on("click", this.handleToggleClick), this.overlay.on("click", this.closeMenu), $(window).on("keydown", this.keyDown), this.lottieContainer.on("mouseenter", function() {
            this.logoLottie.setDirection(1), this.logoLottie.play()
        }.bind(this)), this.lottieContainer.on("mouseleave", function() {
            this.logoLottie.setDirection(-1), this.logoLottie.play()
        }.bind(this));
        var $logos = this.el.find(".header__logo__link svg"),
            $lines = this.toggleBtn.find(".line"),
            $menuNav = this.menu.find(".main-nav");
        this.menuZoom = $menuNav.clone().addClass("main-nav--zoom"), $menuNav.after(this.menuZoom), this.headerNav.heroLinks.on("click", function(e) {
            e.preventDefault()
        }).each(function() {
            $(this).parent().append($(this).clone().addClass("hero-link--full"))
        }), anime.set($logos.get(), {
            translateY: 200
        }), anime.set($lines.get(), {
            scaleX: 0,
            transition: "none",
            transformOrigin: "right center"
        }), this.el.css("opacity", 1), anime({
            targets: $lines.get(),
            scaleX: 1,
            duration: 500,
            delay: anime.stagger(200, {
                start: 1200
            }),
            easing: "easeOutQuad",
            complete: function() {
                $lines.css({
                    "transform-origin": "",
                    transform: "",
                    transition: ""
                })
            }
        }), anime({
            targets: $logos.get().reverse(),
            translateY: 0,
            delay: anime.stagger(200),
            easing: "easeOutQuad",
            complete: function() {
                $logos.css("transform-origin", "")
            }
        }), $menuNav.on("mouseenter", this.mouseEnter).on("mouseleave", this.mouseLeave).on("mousemove", this.mouseMove).find("li a").mouseenter(function() {
            $(this).parents("li").addClass("hover-active").siblings().addClass("hover-inactive")
        }).mouseleave(function() {
            $(this).parents("li").removeClass("hover-active").siblings().removeClass("hover-inactive")
        })
    }, menu.prototype.createCache = function() {
        this.search = {
            el: this.el.find(".header-menu__search")
        }, this.search.input = this.search.el.find(".input input"), this.search.btn = this.search.el.find(".send-btn"), this.search.line = this.search.el.find(".line"), this.search.el.css("overflow", "hidden"), this.headerNav = {
            el: this.el.find(".header-menu__nav")
        }, this.headerNav.heroLinks = this.headerNav.el.find(".hero-link"), this.social = {
            el: this.el.find(".header-menu__social")
        }, this.social.li = this.social.el.find("li"), this.social.a = this.social.li.find("a"), this.social.li.css("overflow", "hidden")
    }, menu.prototype.handleToggleClick = function() {
        this.el.hasClass("header-open") ? this.closeMenu() : this.openMenu()
    }, menu.prototype.mouseEnter = function(e) {
        var top = (e.pageY - $(e.currentTarget).offset().top) / e.currentTarget.offsetHeight * 100,
            bottom = 94 - top;
        top -= 7, anime.set(this.menuZoom.get(), {
            clipPath: "inset(" + top + "% 0% " + bottom + "% 0%)"
        })
    }, menu.prototype.mouseLeave = function() {
        anime.set(this.menuZoom.get(), {
            clipPath: "inset( 0% 0% 100% 0%)"
        })
    }, menu.prototype.mouseMove = function(e) {
        var top = (e.pageY - $(e.currentTarget).offset().top) / e.currentTarget.offsetHeight * 100,
            bottom = 94 - top;
        top -= 7, anime.set(this.menuZoom.get(), {
            clipPath: "inset(" + top + "% 0% " + bottom + "% 0%)"
        })
    }, menu.prototype.openMenu = function() {
        this.toSlide = $("#content, #footer"), this.animating = !0, this.isOpen = !0, this.overlay.delay(400).fadeIn(2500), anime.set(this.menu[0], {
            opacity: 0
        }), this.menu.css("display", "block"), window.innerWidth > app.LG_BREAKPOINT ? (anime.set(this.menu[0], {
            opacity: 1,
            translateX: this.menu.width()
        }), $("body").hasClass("page-template-page-work") || anime({
            targets: this.toSlide.get(),
            translateX: -1 * (this.menu.width() - 100),
            duration: 900,
            delay: 100,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.menu.get(),
            translateX: 0,
            duration: 900,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        })) : anime({
            targets: this.menu.get(),
            opacity: 1,
            duration: 500,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), this.social.li.css("overflow", "hidden"), anime.set([this.search.input[0], this.search.btn[0]].concat(this.social.a.get()), {
            translateY: "100%"
        }), anime.set(this.headerNav.heroLinks.get(), {
            translateY: "100%",
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set(this.search.line[0], {
            transformOrigin: "0 0 0",
            scaleX: 0
        }), this.el.addClass("header-open").removeClass("header-fixed"), anime({
            targets: this.toggleBtn.get(),
            scale: [.5, 1],
            rotate: "360deg",
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint",
            complete: function() {
                $("body").css({
                    overflow: "hidden"
                }), this.animating = !1
            }.bind(this)
        }), anime({
            targets: [this.search.input[0], this.search.btn[0]],
            translateY: 0,
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint",
            delay: anime.stagger(300)
        }), anime({
            targets: this.search.line[0],
            scaleX: 1,
            duration: 1500,
            easing: "easeInOutCirc",
            delay: 200
        }), anime({
            targets: this.headerNav.heroLinks.get(),
            translateY: 0,
            opacity: 1,
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeInOutExpo",
            delay: anime.stagger(150, {
                start: 100
            })
        }), anime({
            targets: this.social.a.get(),
            translateY: 0,
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeInOutExpo",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: 800
            }),
            complete: function() {
                this.social.li.css("overflow", "")
            }.bind(this)
        })
    }, menu.prototype.closeMenu = function() {
        this.el.addClass("header-closing"), this.overlay.fadeOut(300), this.animating = !0, this.social.li.css("overflow", "hidden"), anime({
            targets: this.toggleBtn.get(),
            scale: [.6, 1],
            rotate: "0deg",
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: [this.search.btn[0], this.search.input[0]],
            translateY: "100%",
            duration: 600,
            easing: "easeInQuint",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                start: 200
            }),
            complete: function() {
                this.animating = !1, window.innerWidth > app.LG_BREAKPOINT ? ($("body").hasClass("page-template-page-work") || anime({
                    targets: this.toSlide.get(),
                    translateX: 0,
                    duration: 600,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                }), anime({
                    targets: this.menu.get(),
                    translateX: this.menu.width(),
                    duration: 600,
                    easing: "easeInOutQuint",
                    complete: function() {
                        this.menu.css({
                            display: "none",
                            opacity: ""
                        }), $("body").css({
                            overflow: ""
                        }), this.isOpen = !1, this.el.trigger("menu-closed"), this.el.removeClass("header-closing"), this.el.removeClass("header-open"), this.handleScroll()
                    }.bind(this)
                })) : anime({
                    targets: this.menu.get(),
                    opacity: 0,
                    duration: 300,
                    easing: "easeInQuint",
                    complete: function() {
                        this.menu.css({
                            display: "none",
                            opacity: ""
                        }), $("body").css({
                            overflow: ""
                        }), this.isOpen = !1, this.el.trigger("menu-closed"), this.el.removeClass("header-closing"), this.el.removeClass("header-open"), this.handleScroll()
                    }.bind(this)
                })
            }.bind(this)
        }), anime({
            targets: this.search.line[0],
            scaleX: 0,
            duration: 400,
            easing: "easeInCirc",
            delay: 600
        }), anime({
            targets: this.headerNav.heroLinks.get().reverse(),
            translateY: "100%",
            opacity: 0,
            duration: 400,
            easing: "easeInOutExpo",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger)
        }), anime({
            targets: this.social.a.get().reverse(),
            translateY: "100%",
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeInOutExpo",
            delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger)
        })
    }, menu.prototype.keyDown = function(event) {
        if ("Escape" == event.key && !this.animating && this.isOpen) return this.closeMenu(), !1;
        "m" != event.key || null != event.target.type || this.animating || this.handleToggleClick()
    }, menu.prototype.handleScroll = function() {
        var prevScroll = this.scrollTop;
        this.scrollTop = Math.max($("html").scrollTop(), $("body").scrollTop()), 50 < this.scrollTop ? this.el.addClass("header-fixed") : this.el.removeClass("header-fixed"), this.scrollTop < prevScroll || this.scrollTop < 100 ? this.el.removeClass("pull-up") : this.el.addClass("pull-up")
    }, menu.prototype.destroy = function() {
        $("body").hasClass("page-template-page-work") || anime.set(this.toSlide.get(), {
            translateX: 0
        }), $(window).off("keydown", this.keyDown), this.overlay.off("click", this.closeMenu), this.toggleBtn.off("click", this.handleToggleClick), $(window).off("scroll", this.handleScroll)
    }, menu.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "handleScroll", "destroy", "handleToggleClick", "openMenu", "closeMenu", "createCache", "keyDown", "mouseEnter", "mouseLeave", "mouseMove"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Menu = menu
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function form(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.filters = this.el.find(".filters"), this.keyword = this.el.find("input[name=keyword]"), this.newsType = this.el.find("select[name=news-type]"), this.newsCategory = this.el.find("select[name=news-category]"), this.newsListing = this.el.next(".news-listing"), this.loadMore = this.newsListing.find(".load-more-btn"), this.newsItemsBlock = this.newsListing.find(".news-items.dynamic"), this.cachedXHR = null, this.hammer = new Hammer.Manager(this.loadMore[0]), this.postTag = null, this.paged = 1, this.animationInstances = [], this.cancelToken = axios.CancelToken, this.source = null, this.tagCancelToken = axios.CancelToken, this.tagSource = null, this.init()
    }
    form.prototype.init = function() {
        var that = this;
        this.keyword.on("keyup", function() {
            that.paged = 1, that.postTag = null, that.handleFormSubmit()
        }), this.newsType.on("change", function() {
            that.paged = 1, that.postTag = null, that.handleFormSubmit()
        }), this.newsType.chosen().on("chosen:showing_dropdown", function() {
            var el = $(this);
            el.parents(".form-field").hasClass("active") || el.parents(".form-field").addClass("active")
        }).chosen().on("chosen:hiding_dropdown", function() {
            var el = $(this);
            el.parents(".form-field").hasClass("active") && el.parents(".form-field").removeClass("active")
        }), this.newsCategory.chosen().on("chosen:showing_dropdown", function() {
            var el = $(this);
            el.parents(".form-field").hasClass("active") || el.parents(".form-field").addClass("active")
        }).chosen().on("chosen:hiding_dropdown", function() {
            var el = $(this);
            el.parents(".form-field").hasClass("active") && el.parents(".form-field").removeClass("active")
        }), this.newsCategory.on("change", function() {
            that.paged = 1, that.postTag = null, that.handleFormSubmit()
        }), this.newsListing.on("click", ".news-post-tag", function(e) {
            e.preventDefault(), that.paged = 1, that.postTag = $(this).data("slug"), that.handleFormSubmit()
        }), this.loadMore.on("click", function() {
            this.cachedXHR || that.paged++, that.handleFormSubmit(), this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout)
        }).on("mouseenter", function() {
            that.paged++, this.cachedXHR = this.getXHRRequest(), this.timeout = setTimeout(function() {
                this.handleFormSubmit(), this.timeout = null
            }.bind(this), app.holdTime)
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseleave", function() {
            this.timeout && (this.paged--, clearTimeout(this.timeout), this.timeout = null)
        }.bind(this)), this.hammer.add(new Hammer.Press({
            event: "press",
            pointer: 1,
            threshold: 5,
            time: app.holdTime
        })), this.hammer.on("press", function(event) {
            that.paged++, this.handleFormSubmit()
        }.bind(this))
    }, form.prototype.handleFormSubmit = function() {
        this.cachedXHR ? this.cachedXHR.then(this.propogateData) : this.getXHRRequest().then(this.propogateData)
    }, form.prototype.propogateData = function(response) {
        var that = this;
        this.cachedXHR = null;
        var content = $(response.data.content);
        this.filters.removeClass("filters-loading"), 1 < this.paged ? this.newsItemsBlock.append(content) : this.newsItemsBlock.html(content), content.each(function(index, item) {
            if ($(item).hasClass("o-wrk-blc__slider__slide")) {
                var instance = new app.AnimateNewsItem($(item), !0),
                    inviewInstance = InView(item, function(inview) {
                        inview && (this.destroy(), instance.reveal())
                    });
                that.animationInstances.push(inviewInstance)
            }
        }), response.data.total_result < response.data.posts_per_page ? this.loadMore.hide() : this.loadMore.show()
    }, form.prototype.getXHRRequest = function() {
        return this.source && this.source.cancel(), this.source = this.cancelToken.source(), this.filters.addClass("filters-loading"), axios({
            cancelToken: this.source.token,
            method: "post",
            url: apiroutes.news,
            data: {
                keyword: this.keyword.val(),
                type: this.newsType.val(),
                category: this.newsCategory.val(),
                tag: this.postTag,
                paged: this.paged
            }
        })
    }, form.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.el.off("submit", this.handleFormSubmit), this.keyword.off("keyup"), this.newsType.off("change"), this.newsCategory.off("change"), this.newsListing.off("click", ".news-post-tag"), this.loadMore.off("click"), this.animationInstances.forEach(function(item) {
            item.destroy()
        })
    }, form.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["destroy", "init", "handleFormSubmit", "getXHRRequest", "propogateData"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.NewsForm = form
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function NextProject(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.isPlaying = !1, this.timerRunning = null, this.XHRloading = !1, this.isExpertise = $("body").hasClass("single-expertise"), this.init()
    }
    NextProject.prototype.init = function() {
        var that = this,
            loader = this.el.find(".loader .inner")[0],
            postId = this.el.data("post_id"),
            postType = this.el.data("post_type"),
            projectPostId = this.el.find(".link a").data("post_id"),
            link = this.el.find(".link a").attr("href");
        Barba.Pjax.Cache.set(link, Barba.Utils.xhr(link)), this.el.on("click", this.openNextProject), this.XHRloading || (this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            var inviewContext = this;
            if (isInView) {
                if (!that.isPlaying)
                    if (that.isPlaying = !0, that.timerRunning) that.timerRunning.play();
                    else {
                        var loadedHTML = null;
                        that.XHRloading = !0, that.timerRunning = anime({
                            targets: loader,
                            width: ["0%", "100%"],
                            duration: 8e3,
                            easing: "linear",
                            complete: function() {
                                that.timerRunning = null, that.isPlaying = !1;
                                var oldContent = that.el.children(),
                                    newContent = $(loadedHTML);
                                newContent.css("opacity", 0), that.el.append(newContent), anime({
                                    targets: oldContent.get(),
                                    opacity: 0,
                                    easing: "easeInOutQuint"
                                }), anime({
                                    targets: newContent.get(),
                                    opacity: 1,
                                    easing: "easeInOutQuint",
                                    complete: function() {
                                        that.el.css("height", ""), oldContent.remove(), that.el.off("click", that.openNextProject), that.init()
                                    }
                                })
                            }.bind(that)
                        }), axios({
                            method: "post",
                            url: apiroutes.nextproject,
                            data: {
                                post_id: [postId, projectPostId],
                                post_type: postType
                            }
                        }).then(function(response) {
                            var data = response.data;
                            inviewContext.destroy(), that.XHRloading = !1, that.el.css("height", that.el.height()), $(loadedHTML = data).find(".img-inner").each(function(index, item) {
                                var imgSrc = $(item).css("background-image").match(/url\(["']?([^"']*)["']?\)/)[1];
                                $("<img/>", {
                                    src: imgSrc
                                }).one("load", function() {})
                            })
                        }.bind(that))
                    }
            } else that.isPlaying && that.timerRunning && (that.isPlaying = !1, that.timerRunning.pause())
        }))
    }, NextProject.prototype.openNextProject = function(e) {
        e.preventDefault(), this.isPlaying = !1, this.timerRunning.pause();
        var link = this.el.find(".link a").attr("href");
        Barba.Pjax.Cache.get(link).then(function(data) {
            $(data).find(".carousel__imgs-slide .img").each(function(index, item) {
                var imgSrc = $(item).css("background-image").match(/url\(["']?([^"']*)["']?\)/)[1];
                $("<img/>", {
                    src: imgSrc
                })
            })
        }), window.menu.el.removeClass("header-fixed"), $("body").css({
            overflow: "hidden"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.el.prev().get(),
            translateY: -1 * window.outerHeight,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: $(".footer-newsletter, .footer").get(),
            translateY: window.outerHeight,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), window.BarbaData = {
            el: null,
            from: "next-project"
        }, anime({
            targets: this.el.find(".link").get(),
            translateY: "-100%",
            opacity: 0,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.el.find("h2").get(),
            translateY: "100%",
            opacity: 0,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.el.find(".link").get(),
            translateY: "-100%",
            opacity: 0,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), this.isExpertise ? (this.el.find(".img-inner").addClass("morph"), anime({
            targets: this.el.find(".overlay").get(),
            backgroundColor: "rgba(0,0,0,0)",
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        })) : anime({
            targets: this.el.find(".overlay").get(),
            backgroundColor: "rgba(0,0,0, 0.4)",
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), this.isExpertise ? anime({
            targets: this.el.get(),
            translateY: -1 * this.el[0].getBoundingClientRect().top,
            height: window.outerWidth < app.MD_BREAKPOINT ? "692px" : "700px",
            easing: "easeInOutQuint",
            complete: function() {
                Barba.Pjax.goTo(link), $("body").css({
                    overflow: ""
                })
            }
        }) : anime({
            targets: this.el.get(),
            translateY: -1 * this.el[0].getBoundingClientRect().top,
            height: window.outerWidth < app.MD_BREAKPOINT ? window.innerHeight : "667px",
            easing: "easeInOutQuint",
            complete: function() {
                Barba.Pjax.goTo(link), $("body").css({
                    overflow: ""
                })
            }
        })
    }, NextProject.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.inviewInstance && this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.el.off("click", this.openNextProject)
    }, NextProject.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "openNextProject"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.NextProject = NextProject
}(), String.prototype.padStart || (String.prototype.padStart = function(targetLength, padString) {
    return targetLength >>= 0, padString = String(void 0 !== padString ? padString : " "), this.length >= targetLength ? String(this) : ((targetLength -= this.length) > padString.length && (padString += padString.repeat(targetLength / padString.length)), padString.slice(0, targetLength) + String(this))
});

! function() {
    function PopupHold(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.id = this.el.data("popup-hold"), this.timeout = null, this.hammer = new Hammer.Manager(this.el[0]), this.init()
    }
    PopupHold.prototype.init = function() {
        $(this.el.data("popup-hold")).css("display", "none"), this.el.on("mouseenter", function() {
            this.timeout = setTimeout(function() {
                this.timeout = null, $(window).trigger("resize"), $.fancybox.open($(this.id))
            }.bind(this), app.holdTime)
        }.bind(this)).on("mouseleave", function() {
            this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout)
        }.bind(this)).on("click", function(e) {
            this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout), e.preventDefault(), $(window).trigger("resize"), $.fancybox.open($(this.id))
        }.bind(this)), this.hammer.add(new Hammer.Press({
            event: "press",
            pointer: 1,
            threshold: 5,
            time: app.holdTime
        })), this.hammer.on("press", function(event) {
            this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout), $(window).trigger("resize"), $.fancybox.open($(this.id))
        }.bind(this))
    }, PopupHold.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.hammer.destroy(), this.timeout && clearTimeout(this.timeout), this.el.off("click mouseenter mouseleave")
    }, PopupHold.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.PopupHold = PopupHold
}();

! function() {
    function RelatedSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slidesContainer = this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__slides"), this.slides = this.slidesContainer.children(), this.pagination = this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__foot .wrapper"), this.initSlides = null, this.domCache = this.el.clone(), this.current = 0, this.init()
    }
    RelatedSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.pagination.append(app.getSliderPagination("0" + this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.el.removeClass("uninitialized").addClass("desktop"), this.slidesContainer.addClass("owl-carousel").owlCarousel({
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            margin: 12,
            smartSpeed: 500,
            autoWidth: !0,
            responsive: {
                767: {
                    margin: 30
                }
            },
            onRefreshed: function() {
                this.resize()
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: function(event) {
                this.current = event.item.index, this.updatePagination(this.current)
            }.bind(this)
        }), this.inView(), this.resize()
    }, RelatedSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var slideAnimInstances = [],
            $progressLine = this.el.find(".s-prog__line, .s-prog__marker"),
            $sliderNum = this.el.find(".s-prog__count").css({
                overflow: "hidden"
            }).wrapInner("<span/>").children().css({
                display: "block"
            }).get(),
            owlSlides = this.slidesContainer.find(".owl-item"),
            winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            slidesInView = owlSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
                var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
            });
        slidesInView.each(function(index, slide) {
            slideAnimInstances.push(new app.AnimateNewsItem($(slide))), anime.set(slide, {
                translateY: "100%"
            })
        }), anime.set($sliderNum, {
            translateY: "100%"
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.slidesContainer[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateY: 0,
                duration: 1500,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(200, {
                    start: 400
                })
            }), slideAnimInstances.forEach(function(item, index) {
                setTimeout(function() {
                    item.reveal()
                }, 100 * index)
            }), anime({
                targets: $progressLine.get(),
                width: function(el) {
                    return [0, el.offsetWidth]
                },
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: $sliderNum,
                translateY: "0%",
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1600,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }))
        })
    }, RelatedSlider.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeInQuint"
        })
    }, RelatedSlider.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.paginationMarker && (this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.updatePagination(this.current))
    }, RelatedSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.el.addClass("uninitialized").removeClass("desktop").html(this.domCache.html())
    }, RelatedSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "updatePagination", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.RelatedSlider = RelatedSlider
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function ScrollIndicator(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.lastScroll = window.scrollY / (document.body.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight) * 100, this.lottie = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.el[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: app.lottie.scrollIndicator
        }), this.lottie.addEventListener("enterFrame", this.enterFrame), this.el.on("click", function() {
            $("body, html").animate({
                scrollTop: 0
            })
        }), this.init()
    }
    ScrollIndicator.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), $(window).on("scroll", this.scroll)
    }, ScrollIndicator.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.scroll()
    }, ScrollIndicator.prototype.scroll = function() {
        var scrollPer = Math.round(window.scrollY / (document.body.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight) * 100);
        scrollPer !== this.lastScroll && (this.lottie.setDirection(scrollPer > this.lastScroll ? 1 : -1), this.lottie.play(), this.lastScroll = scrollPer)
    }, ScrollIndicator.prototype.enterFrame = function(data) {
        var currentScroll = Math.round(data.currentTime / data.totalTime * 100);
        this.lottie.setSpeed(Math.max(Math.abs(this.lastScroll - currentScroll), 1)), currentScroll == this.lastScroll && this.lottie.pause()
    }, ScrollIndicator.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "resize", "scroll", "enterFrame"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.ScrollIndicator = ScrollIndicator
}();
var app = app || {};

    function SoundCloud(el) {

            autoplay: !1,
            controls: !1
        }), this.iconAnimation = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.icon[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: app.lottie.playBtn
        }), this.scElement.on("ready", this.init))
    }
    SoundCloud.prototype.init = function() {
        this.button.on("click", function() {
            this.isPlaying ? (this.isPlaying = !1, this.scElement.pause(), this.iconAnimation.setDirection(-1), this.iconAnimation.play()) : (this.isPlaying = !0, this.scElement.play(), this.iconAnimation.setDirection(1), this.iconAnimation.goToAndStop(400))
        }.bind(this))
    }, SoundCloud.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.button.off("click"), this.scElement && this.scElement.destroy(), this.iconAnimation && this.iconAnimation.destroy()
    }, SoundCloud.prototype.createBounds = function() {

            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.SoundCloud = SoundCloud

! function() {
    function SplashScreen(callback) {
        this.createBounds(), this.callback = callback, this.el = $(".splash-scr"), this.progress = this.el.find(".splash-scr__value")[0], this.logo = this.el.find(".splash-scr__logo"), this.loaded = !1, this.lottie = lottie.loadAnimation({
            container: this.logo[0],
            renderer: "svg",
            loop: !1,
            autoplay: !1,
            animationData: window.lottie_loader,
            rendererSettings: {
                className: "lottie-hold-button"
            }
        }), this.init()
    }
    SplashScreen.prototype.init = function() {
        clearInterval(app.splashScreenLoader), this.loaded = !0;
        var done = parseInt(this.progress.innerHTML),
            playProgress = setInterval(function() {
                var mappedValue = Math.max(Math.ceil(Math.min(this.lottie.currentFrame, 270) / 270 * 100), done),
                    played = Math.max(Math.ceil(this.lottie.currentFrame / this.lottie.totalFrames * 100), done);
                this.progress.innerHTML = mappedValue, 100 === played && (clearInterval(playProgress), setTimeout(function() {
                    anime({
                        targets: this.progress,
                        opacity: 0,
                        translateY: "-150px",
                        easing: "easeInOutQuad",
                        duration: 300,
                        complete: function() {
                            this.callback()
                        }.bind(this)
                    }), anime({
                        targets: this.el.get(),
                        translateY: "100%",
                        easing: "easeInOutQuint",
                        duration: 600,
                        delay: 300,
                        complete: function() {
                            this.el.css("display", "none")
                        }.bind(this)
                    })
                }.bind(this), 300))
            }.bind(this));
        anime.set(this.progress, {
            transition: "none"
        }), CookiesHelper.get("not-first-load") && this.lottie.setSpeed(8), this.lottie.play(), CookiesHelper.eraseCookie("not-first-load")
    }, SplashScreen.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.SplashScreen = SplashScreen
}();

! function() {
    function Sticky(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.instance = null, this.mode = window.innerWidth > app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT ? app.DESKTOP : app.MOBILE, this.init()
    }
    Sticky.prototype.init = function() {
        var $parent = this.el.parent();
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.mode === app.DESKTOP && (this.instance = new hcSticky(this.el[0], {
            stickTo: $parent[0]
        }), setTimeout(function() {
            this.instance.refresh()
        }.bind(this), 1e3))
    }, Sticky.prototype.resize = function() {
        if (window.innerWidth > app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.MOBILE) {
            var $parent = this.el.parent();
            this.mode = app.DESKTOP, this.instance = new hcSticky(this.el[0], {
                stickTo: $parent[0]
            }), setTimeout(function() {
                this.instance.refresh()
            }.bind(this), 1e3)
        } else window.innerWidth <= app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.DESKTOP && (this.mode = app.MOBILE, this.instance && this.instance.destroy(), this.instance = null)
    }, Sticky.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.instance && this.instance.destroy()
    }, Sticky.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "resize"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Sticky = Sticky
}();
var app = app || {};

    function TeamBlcSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slider = this.el.find(".team-blc__slides"), this.slides = this.slider.find(".team-blc__slide"), this.pagination = this.el.find(".team-blc__foot"), this.initSlides = this.slides, this.domCache = this.el.clone(), this.init()
    }
    TeamBlcSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized"), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.slider.owlCarousel({
            loop: !1,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            autoWidth: !0,
            margin: 5,
            responsive: {
                991: {
                    margin: 61
                }
            },
            onInitialized: function() {
                this.initSlides = this.slider.find(".owl-item"), this.resize()
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: function(event) {
                this.updatePagination(event.item.index)
            }.bind(this)
        }), this.pagination.css("opacity", 0).append(app.getSliderPagination(this.slides.length < 9 ? "0" : "" + this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.inView()
    }, TeamBlcSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var that = this,
            $sliderNum = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__count").wrapInner("<span/>").children().get();
        app.wrapWords($sliderNum);
        var winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            slidesInView = this.initSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
                var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
            });
        anime.set(slidesInView.get(), {
            translateX: function(item, index) {
                return (index + 1) * (1.5 * winWidth)
            },
            clipPath: "inset(0 0 0 100%)",
            scale: function(item, index) {
                return 2 * (index + 1)
            }
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateX: 0,
                scale: 1,
                clipPath: {
                    value: "inset(0% 0% 0% 0%)",
                    duration: 2700
                },
                duration: 2500,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: 600
            }), anime({
                targets: that.pagination.get(),
                opacity: 1,
                duration: 300,
                delay: 1100,
                complete: function() {
                    that.pagination.css("opacity", "")
                }
            }), anime({
                targets: that.el.find(".s-prog__line").get(),
                width: [0, "100%"],
                duration: 1500,
                delay: 900,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: $sliderNum,
                translateY: 0,
                duration: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(150, {
                    start: 1e3
                })
            }))
        })
    }, TeamBlcSlider.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        })
    }, TeamBlcSlider.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.paginationMarker && (this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.updatePagination(this.current))
    }, TeamBlcSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.slider.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.el.addClass("uninitialized").html(this.domCache.html())
    }, TeamBlcSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView", "resize"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.TeamBlcSlider = TeamBlcSlider

    }
    Ticker.prototype.init = function() {
        this.inView(), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.resize()
    }, Ticker.prototype.inView = function() {
        this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && this.destroy()
        })
    }, Ticker.prototype.resize = function() {
        if (window.innerWidth > app.LG_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.MOBILE) this.mode = app.DESKTOP, this.el.jTicker();
        else if (window.innerWidth <= app.LG_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.DESKTOP) {
            this.mode = app.MOBILE;
            var cloneToReplace = this.cache.clone();
            this.el.replaceWith(cloneToReplace), this.el = cloneToReplace, this.el.off("webkitTransitionEnd otransitionend oTransitionEnd msTransitionEnd transitionend")
        }
    }, Ticker.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.el.off("webkitTransitionEnd otransitionend oTransitionEnd msTransitionEnd transitionend")
    }, Ticker.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView", "resize"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.Ticker = Ticker
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function WorkDetailSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slider = this.el.find("#imageSlides"), this.slides = this.slider.find(".MS__slide__img"), this.loader = this.el.find(".MS__foot .loader"), this.animation = null, this.init()
    }
    WorkDetailSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        this.el.removeClass("uninitialized"), $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.slider.owlCarousel({
            loop: !0,
            center: !1,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            autoplay: !0,
            autoplayTimeout: 6e3,
            items: 1,
            onInitialized: function() {
                this.resize(), this.updateLoader()
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: function(event) {
                this.updateLoader()
            }.bind(this)
        }), this.inView()
    }, WorkDetailSlider.prototype.inView = function() {
        var that = this,
            $slide = this.el.find(".MS__slide"),
            $c = $slide.find("p.category"),
            $p = $slide.find("p:not(.category)"),
            $h2 = $slide.find("h2"),
            $line = $slide.find(".line"),
            $img = $slide.find(".MS__slide__img"),
            $tSplit = Splitting({
                target: $h2.get(),
                by: "chars"
            }),
            $cSplit = Splitting({
                target: $c.get(),
                by: "lines"
            }),
            $pSplit = Splitting({
                target: $p.get(),
                by: "lines"
            });
        $slide.addClass("--toAnimate --no-transition"), requestAnimationFrame(function() {
            $slide.first().removeClass("--no-transition")
        }.bind(this)), app.wrapWords($tSplit[0].chars), app.wrapLines($pSplit[0].lines), app.wrapLines($cSplit[0].lines), anime.set($img.get(), {
            scale: 2
        }), this.loader.css("opacity", 0), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.el[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), requestAnimationFrame(function() {
                $slide.removeClass("--toAnimate").show()
            }), anime({
                targets: $img.get(),
                scale: [1.5, 1],
                duration: 1500,
                easing: "easeInOutCubic"
            }), anime({
                targets: $line.get(),
                width: [0, $line.width()],
                opacity: [1, 1],
                duration: 1e3,
                delay: 2e3,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: that.loader.get(),
                width: [0, that.loader.width()],
                opacity: [1, 1],
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 3e3,
                easing: "easeInOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: $tSplit[0].chars,
                translateY: ["100%", 0],
                duration: 1400,
                easing: "easeOutElastic(1, 0.45)",
                delay: anime.stagger(app.animationStagger, {
                    start: 1200
                })
            }), $pSplit[0].lines.forEach(function(line, index) {
                anime({
                    targets: line,
                    translateY: ["100%", 0],
                    duration: 1e3,
                    easing: "easeOutQuint",
                    delay: 2e3 + 100 * index
                })
            }), $cSplit[0].lines.forEach(function(line, index) {
                anime({
                    targets: line,
                    translateY: ["100%", 0],
                    duration: 1e3,
                    easing: "easeOutQuint",
                    delay: 1800 + 100 * index
                })
            }))
        })
    }, WorkDetailSlider.prototype.updateLoader = function() {
        this.animation && this.animation.pause();
        var loader = this.loader.find(".inner").get();
        anime({
            targets: loader,
            width: "0%",
            duration: 300,
            easing: "easeOutQuint",
            complete: function() {
                this.animation = anime({
                    targets: loader,
                    width: ["0%", "100%"],
                    duration: 5500,
                    easing: "linear"
                })
            }.bind(this)
        })
    }, WorkDetailSlider.prototype.resize = function() {}, WorkDetailSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.slider.trigger("destroy.owl.carousel"), $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.inviewInstance.destroy()
    }, WorkDetailSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.WorkDetailSlider = WorkDetailSlider
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function OurWorkSliderDesktop(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slidesContainer = this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__slides"), this.slides = this.slidesContainer.children(), this.pagination = this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__foot .wrapper"), this.initSlides = null, this.domCache = this.el.clone(), this.current = 0, this.init()
    }
    OurWorkSliderDesktop.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.pagination.append(app.getSliderPagination(this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.slides.each(function(index, item) {
            item.setAttribute("data-index", index)
        }), this.el.removeClass("uninitialized").addClass("desktop"), this.slidesContainer.addClass("owl-carousel").owlCarousel({
            loop: !0,
            center: !0,
            dots: !1,
            nav: !1,
            margin: 30,
            smartSpeed: 500,
            autoWidth: !0,
            onRefreshed: function() {
                this.resize(), this.initSlides = this.slidesContainer.find(".owl-item")
            }.bind(this),
            onTranslated: function(event) {
                this.current = event.item.index - Math.floor(this.slides.length / 2) - 1, this.updatePagination(this.initSlides.filter(".center").children().data("index"))
            }.bind(this)
        }), this.inView(), this.resize()
    }, OurWorkSliderDesktop.prototype.inView = function() {
        var slideAnimInstances = [],
            $bg = this.el.closest(".o-wrk-blc").find(".o-wrk-blc__bg"),
            $progressLine = this.el.find(".s-prog__line, .s-prog__marker"),
            $sliderNum = this.el.find(".s-prog__count").css({
                overflow: "hidden"
            }).wrapInner("<span/>").children().css({
                display: "block"
            }).get(),
            owlSlides = this.slidesContainer.find(".owl-item"),
            winWidth = window.outerWidth,
            slidesInView = owlSlides.filter(function(index, slide) {
                var bounds = slide.getBoundingClientRect();
                return 0 <= bounds.left && bounds.right <= winWidth || bounds.left <= 0 && 0 <= bounds.right || bounds.left <= winWidth && bounds.right >= winWidth
            });
        slidesInView.each(function(index, slide) {
            slideAnimInstances.push(new app.AnimateNewsItem($(slide))), anime.set(slide, {
                translateY: "100%"
            })
        }), anime.set($sliderNum, {
            translateY: "100%"
        }), anime.set($bg.get(), {
            scaleY: "0",
            transformOrigin: "center bottom"
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.slidesContainer[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: $bg.get(),
                scaleY: 1,
                duration: 2e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: slidesInView.get(),
                translateY: 0,
                duration: 1500,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(200, {
                    start: 400
                })
            }), slideAnimInstances.forEach(function(item, index) {
                setTimeout(function() {
                    item.reveal()
                }, 100 * index)
            }), anime({
                targets: $progressLine.get(),
                width: function(el) {
                    return [0, el.offsetWidth]
                },
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }), anime({
                targets: $sliderNum,
                translateY: "0%",
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1600,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }))
        })
    }, OurWorkSliderDesktop.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 2e3,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 600,
            easing: "easeOutQuint"
        })
    }, OurWorkSliderDesktop.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.paginationMarker && (this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.updatePagination(this.current))
    }, OurWorkSliderDesktop.prototype.destroy = function() {
        $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.el.addClass("uninitialized").removeClass("desktop").html(this.domCache.html())
    }, OurWorkSliderDesktop.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "updatePagination", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.OurWorkSliderDesktop = OurWorkSliderDesktop
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function OurWorkSliderMobile(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.slidesContainer = this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__slides"), this.slides = this.slidesContainer.children(), this.pagination = this.el.find(".o-wrk-blc__slider__foot .wrapper"), this.current = 0, this.animating = !1, this.domCache = this.el.clone(), this.hammertime = new Hammer(this.el[0]), this.init()
    }
    OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.pagination.append(app.getSliderPagination("0" + this.slides.length)), this.paginationMarker = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__marker"), this.paginationCurrent = this.pagination.find(".s-prog__current .item"), this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.el.removeClass("uninitialized").addClass("mobile"), this.slides.not(":nth-child(1)").css({
            display: "none"
        }), this.hammertime.on("swipe", function(ev) {
            ev.deltaX < 0 ? this.next() : this.prev()
        }.bind(this)), this.hammertime.on("pan", this.panStart), this.hammertime.on("panend", this.panEnd), this.inView(), this.resize()
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.inView = function() {
        var $firstSlide = this.slides.first(),
            $slideImage = $firstSlide.find(".image"),
            $body = $firstSlide.find(".body"),
            $type = $firstSlide.find(".type"),
            $progressLine = this.el.find(".s-prog__line"),
            $sliderNum = this.el.find(".s-prog__count").wrapInner("<span/>").children().get();
        app.wrapWords($sliderNum), anime.set($slideImage[0], {
            translateX: 40,
            rotateY: "60deg",
            translateZ: 100,
            opacity: 0
        }), anime.set($body[0], {
            translateX: "100%"
        }), anime.set($type[0], {
            translateY: "100%",
            opacity: 0
        }), this.inviewInstance = InView(this.slidesContainer[0], function(isInView) {
            isInView && (this.destroy(), anime({
                targets: $slideImage.get(),
                translateX: [40, 0],
                rotateY: ["60deg", "0deg"],
                translateZ: [100, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                easing: "easeOutCirc",
                duration: 300,
                delay: 200
            }), anime({
                targets: $body.get(),
                translateX: ["100%", 0],
                easing: "easeOutCirc",
                duration: 1e3,
                delay: 400
            }), anime({
                targets: $type.get(),
                translateY: ["100%", 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                easing: "easeOutCubic",
                duration: 1e3,
                delay: 500
            }), anime({
                targets: $sliderNum,
                translateY: 0,
                duration: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint",
                delay: anime.stagger(150, {
                    start: 1400
                })
            }), anime({
                targets: $progressLine.get(),
                width: function(el) {
                    return [0, el.offsetWidth]
                },
                duration: 2e3,
                delay: 1e3,
                easing: "easeOutQuint"
            }))
        })
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.panStart = function(ev) {
        this.animating || anime({
            targets: this.slides.eq(this.current).get(),
            translateZ: .05 * ev.deltaX,
            translateX: .05 * ev.deltaX,
            opacity: 1,
            duration: 0
        })
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.panEnd = function(ev) {
        setTimeout(function() {
            this.animating || (this.animating = !0, anime({
                targets: this.slides.eq(this.current).get(),
                translateZ: 0,
                translateX: 0,
                opacity: 1,
                easing: "easeOutQuad",
                duration: 300,
                complete: function() {
                    this.animating = !1
                }.bind(this)
            }))
        }.bind(this), 0)
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.next = function() {
        if (this.current !== this.slides.length - 1 && !this.animating) {
            var _prev = this.current;
            this.current++, this.animating = !0, this.updatePagination(this.current), anime({
                targets: this.slides.eq(_prev).get(),
                translateZ: -160,
                translateX: -120,
                opacity: 0,
                easing: "easeOutQuad",
                duration: 500
            }), anime({
                targets: this.slides.eq(this.current).get(),
                translateZ: [160, 0],
                translateX: [160, 0],
                opacity: {
                    value: [0, 1],
                    duration: 200
                },
                delay: 400,
                easing: "easeOutQuad",
                duration: 500,
                complete: function() {
                    this.animating = !1
                }.bind(this)
            }), this.slides.eq(this.current).css("display", "block"), this.slidesContainer.animate({
                height: this.slides.eq(this.current).height()
            })
        }
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.prev = function() {
        if (0 !== this.current && !this.animating) {
            var _prev = this.current;
            this.current--, this.animating = !0, this.updatePagination(this.current), anime({
                targets: this.slides.eq(_prev).get(),
                translateZ: 160,
                translateX: 160,
                opacity: 0,
                easing: "easeOutQuad",
                duration: 500,
                complete: function() {
                    this.animating = !1, this.slides.eq(_prev).css("display", "none")
                }.bind(this)
            }), anime({
                targets: this.slides.eq(this.current).get(),
                translateZ: [-160, 0],
                translateX: [-120, 0],
                opacity: [0, 1],
                delay: 400,
                duration: 500,
                easing: "easeOutQuad"
            }), this.slidesContainer.animate({
                height: this.slides.eq(this.current).height()
            })
        }
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.updatePagination = function(current) {
        this.paginationCurrent && anime({
            targets: this.paginationCurrent.get(),
            translateY: this.paginationCurrent.height() * current * -1,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeInOutQuint"
        }), anime({
            targets: this.paginationMarker.get(),
            translateX: this.paginationMarker.width() * current,
            duration: 1e3,
            easing: "easeInQuint"
        })
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.resize = function() {
        this.slidesContainer.height(this.slides.eq(this.current).height()), this.paginationMarker && (this.paginationMarker.width(this.pagination.find(".s-prog").width() / this.slides.length), this.updatePagination(this.current))
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.destroy = function() {
        $(window).off("resize", this.resize), this.hammertime.destroy(), this.inviewInstance.destroy(), this.el.addClass("uninitialized").removeClass("mobile").html(this.domCache.html())
    }, OurWorkSliderMobile.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "next", "prev", "resize", "panStart", "panEnd", "updatePagination", "inView"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.OurWorkSliderMobile = OurWorkSliderMobile
}();
var app = app || {};
! function() {
    function OurWorkSlider(el) {
        this.createBounds(), this.el = el, this.mode = window.innerWidth > app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT ? app.DESKTOP : app.MOBILE, this.init()
    }
    OurWorkSlider.prototype.init = function() {
        $(window).on("resize", this.resize), this.instance = this.mode === app.MOBILE ? new app.OurWorkSliderMobile(this.el) : new app.OurWorkSliderDesktop(this.el)
    }, OurWorkSlider.prototype.resize = function() {
        window.innerWidth > app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.MOBILE ? (this.mode = app.DESKTOP, this.instance && this.instance.destroy(), this.instance = new app.OurWorkSliderDesktop(this.el)) : window.innerWidth <= app.MOBILE_BREAKPOINT && this.mode === app.DESKTOP && (this.mode = app.MOBILE, this.instance && this.instance.destroy(), this.instance = new app.OurWorkSliderMobile(this.el))
    }, OurWorkSlider.prototype.destroy = function() {
        this.instance && this.instance.destroy(), $(window).off("resize", this.resize)
    }, OurWorkSlider.prototype.createBounds = function() {
        var that = this;
        ["init", "destroy", "resize"].forEach(function(fn) {
            that[fn] = that[fn].bind(that)
        })
    }, app.OurWorkSlider = OurWorkSlider
}();

    function cf7mailsent(event) {
        for (var inputs = event.detail.inputs, i = 0; i < inputs.length; i++)
            if ("contact_form" == inputs[i].name) {
                var form_value = inputs[i].value,
                    utm_value = $('input[name="utm_source"]').val() + "_" + $('input[name="utm_content"]').val();
                "project" == form_value && gtag("event", "Submit", {
                    event_category: "Enquiry",
                    event_label: utm_value
                }), "career" == form_value && gtag("event", "Submit", {
                    event_category: "JobApp",
                    event_label: utm_value
                });
                break
            }
    }

            youtube: {

                showinfo: 0
            }

        }), $el.dataSticky.each(function(index, el) {

        }), $el.form.each(function(index, el) {
            _instances.push(new app.Form($(el)))

        }), $el.relatedSlider.each(function(index, el) {

            _instances.push(new app.TeamBlcSlider($(el)))
        }), $el.animate.each(function(index, el) {
            _instances.push(new app.AnimateGroup($(el)))
        }), $el.locationFilter.each(function(index, el) {

        }), $el.popupHold.each(function(index, el) {
            _instances.push(new app.PopupHold($(el)))
        }), $el.holdButton.each(function(index, el) {
            _instances.push(new app.HoldButton($(el)))

            _instances.push(new app.AnimateIcon($(el)))
        }), $(window).width() < 767 && $el.awardMobile.each(function(index, el) {
            _instances.push(new app.AwardSliderMobile($(el)))
        });
        var utmObj = function() {
                var vars = {};
                window.location.href.replace(/[?&]+([^=&]+)=([^&]*)/gi, function(m, key, value) {
                    vars[key] = value
                });
                return vars
            }(),
            utmFieldArray = ["utm_campaign", "utm_source", "utm_term", "utm_medium", "utm_content"];
        0 < Object.keys(utmObj).length ? utmFieldArray.forEach(function(utm_field) {
            void 0 !== utmObj[utm_field] && sessionStorage.setItem(utm_field, utmObj[utm_field])
        }) : utmFieldArray.forEach(function(utm_field) {
            var utmField = sessionStorage.getItem(utm_field);
            null != utmField && $("input[name=" + utm_field + "]").val(utmField)
        }), $('[name="page_current_url"]').val(window.location.href), document.addEventListener("wpcf7mailsent", cf7mailsent, !1), $('iframe[src*="youtube"]').parent().fitVids(), _plyrInstances = new Plyr("#content video", {
            controls: !1,
            autoplay: !0,
            autopause: !1
        }), window.BarbaData = {}
    }

    function initStaticComponents() {
        if (initDynamicComponents(), $("body").on("click", "a", function() {
                CookiesHelper.set("not-first-load", !0, 1)
            }), $el.scrollIndicator.each(function(index, el) {
                new app.ScrollIndicator($(el))
            }), $el.cursor.length && (window.cursor = new app.Cursor($el.cursor)), window.menu = new app.Menu($el.header), !app.initialLoad)
            if (app.initialLoad = !0, 0 < window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li.active").length) window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li:not(.active)").addClass("inactive");
            else {
                var newSlug = location.pathname.split("/")[1];
                newSlug && window.menu.el.find(".main-nav a.hero-link[href*=" + newSlug + "]").parent().addClass("active"), window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li.active").length && window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li:not(.active)").addClass("inactive")
            }
        window.setTimeout(function() {
            $(window).trigger("resize")
        }, 1e3), is_touch_device() && $("html").addClass("has-touch"), (!app.detectIE() || 11 < app.detectIE()) && (Barba.Pjax.start(), Barba.Prefetch.init(), window.isBarba = !0, Barba.Dispatcher.on("initStateChange", function() {
            "function" == typeof ga && ga("send", "pageview", location.pathname), window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li").removeClass("active").removeClass("inactive");
            var newSlug = location.pathname.split("/")[1];
            newSlug && window.menu.el.find(".main-nav a.hero-link[href*=" + newSlug + "]").parent().addClass("active"), window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li.active").length && window.menu.el.find(".main-nav li:not(.active)").addClass("inactive"), window.menu.isOpen && window.menu.closeMenu(), window.cursor && window.cursor.resetCursor()
        }), Barba.Dispatcher.on("transitionCompleted", function() {
            $.fancybox.destroy(), _instances.forEach(function(item) {
                item.destroy()
            }), _plyrInstances.destroy(), $("body").removeClass("blur");
            try {
                gtag("config", "UA-49447008-1", {
                    page_title: document.title,
                    page_location: document.location.href,
                    page_path: location.pathname
                })
            } catch (error) {
                console.error("Error with the GTAG", error)
            }
            cacheDom(), screenResize(), initDynamicComponents(), $el.contactForm7.length && _instances.push(new app.ContactForm7($el.contactForm7)), $("#cursor").removeClass("on-slider"), $(window).trigger("resize")
        }), Barba.Pjax.getTransition = function() {
            return app.BarbaTransition
        }, Barba.Pjax.originalPreventCheck = Barba.Pjax.preventCheck)
    }
    window.BarbaData = {}, app.initialLoad = !1, app.rtl = "rtl" === $("html").attr("dir"), app.isIE = !!app.detectIE(), app.isIE && $("body").addClass("isIE isIE-" + app.detectIE()), $(document).ready(function() {
        if (cacheDom(), $(window).on("resize", app.debounce(screenResize, 200)).on("scroll", windowScroll).trigger("resize"), new app.SplashScreen(function() {
                screenResize(), initStaticComponents()
            }), $("body").addClass("js-init"), !CookiesHelper.get("user-consent")) {
            var $cookieBlc = $(".cookies-blc");
            $cookieBlc.show(), $cookieBlc.one("click", ".accept-btn", function(e) {
                e.preventDefault(), CookiesHelper.set("user-consent", 1, 365), $cookieBlc.hide()
            })
        }
    })
}(jQuery, document, window);
